an%3EI%20kept%20thinking%20of%20my%20hypothetical%20wedding%20day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20time%20I%20sat%20down%20to%20write%2C%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20vivid%20and%20hypothetical%20image%20of%20my%20wedding%20day.%20It's%20like%20the%20universe%20wanted%20me%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20gut-wrenching%20idea%20of%20my%20dad%20not%20giving%20me%20away.%20This%20is%20something%20I've%20romanticized%20since%20such%20a%20young%20age.%20A%20vision%20I%20believed%20no%20doubt%20would%20come%20true.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20one%20sleepless%20night%2C%20it%20hit%20me.%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20keepsake%20where%20my%20dad%20and%20I%20could%20write%20letters%2C%20share%20memories%20and%20process%20our%20feelings%2C%20together.%20I%20found%20a%20tatty%20old%20notebook%20and%20wrote%20my%20first%20letter%20to%20him.%20I%20sobbed%20as%20the%20sunrise%20slowly%20peeped%20through%20my%20bedroom%20curtain.%20The%20very%20first%20thing%20I%20asked%20him%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20letter%2C%20ink%20smudged%20with%20tears%2C%20was%20if%20he%20could%20write%20his%20wedding%20speech%20for%20me.%20I%20left%20the%20letter%20in%20the%20cabin%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDad%20responded%20lovingly%2C%20but%20not%20the%20part%20about%20the%20speech.%20Months%20went%20by%2C%20and%20Dad's%20health%20deteriorated.%20As%20expected%2C%20his%20body%20rejected%20the%20chemo.%20There%20was%20no%20sign%20of%20a%20speech%2C%20and%20I%20accepted%20that%20perhaps%20this%20was%20too%20much%20to%20ask.%20It%20got%20to%20the%20point%20where%20he%20started%20to%20lose%20control%20of%20his%20limbs%2C%20and%20couldn't%20talk%2C%20so%20our%20letters%20to%20each%20other%20became%20more%20and%20more%20sparse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%20to%20myself.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20brave%20of%20me%20to%20ask.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222475b2f2-8cba-462c-9d54-48a560096751%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20found%20the%20speech%20he%20wrote%20for%20me%20after%20he%20died%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20hot%20summer's%20morning%2C%20the%20day%20my%20dad%20died%20in%20the%20care%20of%20our%20local%20hospice.%20He'd%20been%20there%20for%20three%20weeks%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20pain%2C%20stabilized%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20morphine%20%E2%80%94%20surrounded%20by%20his%20family.%20He%20clung%20on%2C%20quite%20literally%2C%20for%20dear%20life%2C%20before%20peacefully%20surrendering%20beside%20those%20he%20loved%20most.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20that%20day%2C%20as%20we%20navigated%20the%20flurry%20of%20peace%20lilies%2C%20%26quot%3Bsorry%20for%20your%20loss%26quot%3B%20messages%20and%20a%20stack%20of%20homemade%20lasagnas%20we%20didn't%20have%20the%20appetite%20to%20eat%2C%20we%20came%20across%20his%20will%20in%20a%20pile%20of%20his%20things.%20As%20a%20family%2C%20we%20opened%20it%20together%20around%20the%20kitchen%20table.%20Amongst%20pages%20of%20financial%20practicalities%20and%20funeral%20wishes%2C%20there%20was%20a%20folder%20of%20white%20envelopes%20addressed%20to%20each%20of%20us%20-%20his%20wife%20and%20four%20children.%20On%20the%20front%20of%20mine%20read%20%26quot%3BLar...%26quot%3B.%20On%20the%20back%3A%20%26quot%3BYour%20wedding%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20this%20day%2C%20the%20envelope%20remains%20sealed%2C%20tucked%20away%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20%26quot%3Bdad%20box%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20the%20notebook%20we%20shared%2C%20photo%20albums%20of%20memories%2C%20and%20a%20collection%20of%20swimming%20medals%20he%20wanted%20me%20to%20show%20his%20grandkids%20one%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20I've%20got%20this%20treasured%20sentiment%20to%20be%20shared%20on%20what%20I%20deem%20to%20be%20the%20most%20special%20day%20of%20my%20life%20is%20invaluable%20for%20my%20grieving%20process%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20doesn't%20make%20up%20for%20the%20fact%20he%20won't%20be%20physically%20there%20by%20my%20side%20on%20my%20wedding%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20sit%20alone%20in%20his%20cabin%20often%2C%20soaking%20in%20the%20rays%20of%20sunshine%20glistening%20through%20the%20trees.%20Mug%20of%20tea%20in%20hand%2C%20I%20feel%20comforted%20by%20the%20intuitive%20knowing%20that%20he'll%20always%20be%20with%20me%20in%20some%20capacity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20four%20years%20later%2C%20I%20feel%20glimpses%20of%20those%20peaceful%20moments%20we%20shared%20in%20that%20garden.%20Before%20our%20lives%20turned%20upside%20down.%20For%20those%20moments%2C%20I%20am%20unfathomably%20grateful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELara%20Rodwell%20is%20the%20author%20of%20Guided%20Grief%20Journal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8fd9ada918b51586ceb0f21f010677fa91ddf88d2d45fa0a8d3888a245c4143c%26postID%3D66f2ba068d7e7259bc935829%26postSlug%3Ddad-wrote-wedding-speech-before-death-2024-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.co.uk%252FPrognosis-Peace-Navigating-Discovery-Gratitude%252Fdp%252F1913615316%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20Prognosis%20to%20Peace%3A%20Navigating%20Grief%20through%20Gratitude%2C%20Discovery%20and%20Healing%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20notebook%20she%20shared%20with%20her%20dad.%20Available%20on%20Amazon%20and%20other%20book%20retailers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-wrote-wedding-speech-before-death-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727604782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2c4afce3009a0fac8d3aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-wrote-wedding-speech-before-death-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20dad%20was%20given%20six%20months%20to%20live%20and%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20wanted%20him%20to%20do%20was%20to%20write%20my%20wedding%20speech.%20I%20found%20the%20speech%20after%20he%20died.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(%20Lara%20Rodwell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-wrote-wedding-speech-before-death-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20tax-reducing%20steps%20to%20take%20before%202024%20ends%2C%20according%20to%20%242%20trillion%20wealth%20manager%20BNY%20Mellon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stacks%20of%20cash%20standing%20against%20a%20red%20and%20white%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659769301c5c7b8c9a0e312a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221927%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInvestors%20can%20modify%20the%20timing%20of%20their%20income%20or%20deductions%20to%20reduce%20their%20tax%20bills.%3Cp%3EGetty%2FPM%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAs%202024%20draws%20to%20a%20close%2C%20now%20is%20the%20time%20for%20investors%20to%20review%20their%20tax%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20year%20is%20especially%20important%2C%20as%20new%20legislation%20could%20materially%20change%20tax%20laws.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBNY%20Mellon%20shares%20eight%20ways%20investors%20can%20reduce%20their%20tax%20burden%20for%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20October%20coming%20into%20view%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20time%20to%20sit%20down%20and%20review%20your%20tax%20strategy%20for%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20the%20impacts%20on%20tax%20legislation%20that%20the%20presidential%20election%20could%20have%2C%20this%20is%20an%20especially%20important%20year%20to%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20your%20approach%20to%20minimize%20your%20tax%20burden%2C%20according%20to%20BNY%20Mellon%20Wealth%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20note%2C%20the%20bank%20shared%20eight%20tax-reducing%20actions%20for%20investors%20to%20consider%20before%20the%20tax%20year%20ends%20on%20December%2031st.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3e140d3-0fde-41b5-8d6d-faf655f2f202%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinimize%20income%20tax%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20can%20modify%20the%20timing%20of%20their%20income%20or%20deductions%20to%20reduce%20their%20tax%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20BNY%20Mellon%20says%20to%20consider%20%3Cstrong%3Eaccelerating%20income%20into%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20current%20tax%20rates%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20increase%20in%202025.%20Investors%20can%20accelerate%20income%20by%20exercising%20stock%20options%20and%20realizing%20deferred%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20high%20earners%20may%20want%20to%20defer%20investment%20income%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Eminimize%20their%20net%20investment%20income%20tax%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3E(NIIT)%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20The%20NIIT%20is%20a%203.8%25%20tax%20on%20net%20investment%20income%20for%20individuals%20whose%20income%20(MAGI)%20crosses%20%24200%2C000%20for%20single%20filers%2C%20so%20deferring%20income%20can%20help%20investors%20avoid%20triggering%20the%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20expecting%20income%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20an%20asset%20like%20real%20estate%2C%20BNY%20Mellon%20suggests%20%3Cstrong%3Eelecting%20out%20of%20collecting%20that%20income%20on%20an%20installment%20basis%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20By%20selling%20on%20an%20installment%20basis%2C%20the%20seller%20collects%20payment%20on%20a%20staggered%20timeline%20instead%20of%20all%20at%20once%2C%20resulting%20in%20at%20least%20one%20payment%20after%20the%20tax%20year%20in%20which%20the%20sale%20happens.%20If%20taxes%20increase%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20investors%20who%20use%20the%20installment%20method%20could%20find%20themselves%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20higher%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208e9dbca-e98d-48c3-8c2a-97d98dcdf2e5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERebalance%20your%20portfolio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20consider%20future%20taxes%20on%20your%20investment%20portfolio%2C%20the%20bank%20said.%20%3Cstrong%3ETax-loss%20harvesting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20one%20strategy%20to%20minimize%20capital%20gains%20taxes%20on%20tradable%20securities%20such%20as%20stocks%2C%20bonds%2C%20and%20ETFs.%20Investors%20who%20sell%20an%20asset%20at%20a%20loss%20can%20use%20the%20loss%20to%20offset%20capital%20gains%20on%20another%20investment.%20You%20can%20also%20offset%20personal%20income%20using%20this%20method%20%E2%80%94%20if%20your%20losses%20exceed%20gains%20this%20year%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20difference%20to%20discount%20up%20to%20%243%2C000%20of%20personal%20income.%20Investors%20utilizing%20this%20strategy%20should%20liquidate%20their%20losses%20before%20the%20December%2031%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you're%20using%20the%20tax-loss%20harvesting%20strategy%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Eavoid%20the%20wash-sale%20rule%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20This%20rule%20prohibits%20investors%20from%20selling%20a%20security%20at%20a%20loss%20and%20buying%20back%20the%20same%20investment%20within%2030%20days%20of%20the%20sale.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20recognize%20a%20capital%20loss%20but%20stay%20invested%20in%20the%20security%2C%20consider%20making%20an%20additional%20purchase%20of%20the%20security%20more%20than%2030%20days%20before%20selling%20at%20a%20loss%2C%20the%20note%20said.%20With%202024%20coming%20to%20an%20end%2C%20investors%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20this%2030-day%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f40fcaa0-0d18-42ee-a71b-87ca7cab4298%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetirement%20considerations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBNY%20Mellon%20also%20said%20to%20consider%20%3Cstrong%3Emaxing%20out%20your%20retirement%20accounts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20such%20as%20a%20401(k)%2C%20traditional%20IRA%2C%20Roth%20IRA%2C%20and%20other%20plans.%20Maxing%20out%20your%20contributions%20could%20be%20especially%20pertinent%20this%20year%2C%20as%20BNY%20Mellon%20sees%20potential%20for%20new%20legislation%20to%20limit%20retirement%20account%20contributions%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20over%2050%20years%20of%20age%20making%20%26quot%3Bcatch-up%26quot%3B%20contributions%20can%20add%20an%20additional%20%241%2C000%20to%20a%20Roth%20IRA%20on%20top%20of%20the%20%247%2C000%20limit%2C%20for%20a%20total%20of%20%248%2C000%20this%20year%2C%20the%20bank%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20consider%20%3Cstrong%3Eswitching%20from%20a%20traditional%20IRA%20to%20a%20Roth%20IRA%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20While%20this%20means%20you'll%20owe%20income%20tax%20on%20the%20money%20you%20convert%2C%20your%20assets%20will%20accumulate%20tax-free%20in%20the%20Roth%20IRA%20going%20forward%2C%20according%20to%20the%20note.%20This%20is%20especially%20advantageous%20if%20you%20anticipate%20your%20future%20tax%20rate%20to%20be%20higher%20than%20what%20it%20is%20currently%2C%20as%20eligible%20Roth%20IRA%20withdrawals%20are%20tax-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20if%20eligible%2C%20investors%20should%20ensure%20they%20take%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Erequired%20minimum%20distributions%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efrom%20their%20retirement%20plans.%20After%20a%20certain%20age%2C%20you%20must%20withdraw%20a%20minimum%20amount%20from%20your%20retirement%20account%20to%20avoid%20a%20tax%20penalty%2C%20the%20bank%20said.%20Those%20over%20the%20age%20of%2073%20who%20don't%20take%20the%20required%20minimum%20distribution%20are%20subject%20to%20a%2025%25%20tax%20on%20the%20undrawn%20amount.%20Avoid%20this%20penalty%20by%20double-checking%20your%20required%20minimum%20distribution%20prior%20to%20year-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A