%3Bat%20least%26quot%3B%20a%20say%20in%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20monetary%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20study%20by%20the%20Peterson%20Institute%20of%20International%20Economics%2C%20a%20renowned%20nonpartisan%20think%20tank%2C%20found%20that%20such%20an%20idea%20could%20have%20catastrophic%20economic%20consequences.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.piie.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-09%2Fwp24-20.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy's%20lead%20researchers%3C%2Fa%3E%20dug%20into%20the%20economic%20impact%20of%20three%20of%20Trump's%20campaign%20promises%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mass-deportation-immigraiton-plan-federal-reserve-inflation-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emass%20deportations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjared-golden-10-percent-tariff-bill-trump-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20eroding%20Fed%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20course%20of%20a%20prospective%20Trump%20term%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-campaign-fed-independence-jerome-powell-interes-rates-politics-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eundermining%20the%20central%20bank's%20independence%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20lead%20to%20%24304%20billion%20in%20economic%20losses%2C%20the%20study%20found.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump%20has%20not%20specified%20exactly%20how%20he%20would%20interfere%20in%20the%20Fed%2C%20the%20researchers%20assumed%20he%20is%20successful%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rate-cut-trump-fed-powell-reaction-independence-history-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epressured%20the%20bank%20to%20jack%20up%20economic%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20conducting%20their%20study.%20They%20found%20that%20such%20action%20would%20result%20in%20lower%20GDP%20and%20higher%20inflation%20through%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20authors%2C%20Warwick%20McKibbin%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20PIIE.%20He%20said%20that%20initially%2C%20GDP%20and%20employment%20would%20rise%2C%20but%20that%20inflation%20and%20input%20costs%20would%20go%20up%20soon%20after.%20Eventually%2C%20capital%20would%20flow%20out%20of%20the%20US%2C%20causing%20the%20dollar%20to%20fall%20in%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20the%20party%20at%20the%20front%20and%20the%20hangover%20after%20four%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20McKibbin%20said%20over%20the%20phone.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20by%202028%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-inflation-kamala-harris-election-impact-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%20would%20be%20built%20into%20the%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20an%20additional%202%25%20per%20year%20and%20the%20economy%20would%20shrink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomestic%20producers%20would%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20consequences%20due%20to%20rising%20input%20costs.%20As%20domestic%20goods%20get%20more%20expensive%2C%20workers'%20purchasing%20power%20would%20go%20down%2C%20McKibbin%20said.%20All%20the%20while%2C%20the%20researchers%20argue%20that%20investors%20would%20get%20spooked%20by%20the%20politicized%20Fed%20and%20start%20directing%20their%20capital%20to%20other%20countries%20starting%20around%202026.%20Production%20would%20shift%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20including%20China%2C%20the%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIronically%2C%20it%20means%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20gets%20this%20free%20lunch%20because%20all%20that%20capital%20that%20would%20have%20gone%20into%20building%20America's%20future%20growth%20will%20now%20get%20invested%20somewhere%20else%2C%20mainly%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20China%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Australia%2C%26quot%3B%20McKibbin%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Though%20Trump%20promises%20an%20America%20First%20economic%20agenda%2C%20McKibbin%20said%20that%20taking%20control%20of%20the%20Fed%20would%20get%20him%20the%20opposite%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20study%2C%20the%20economy%20would%20hit%20a%20low%20point%20in%202028%20and%20begin%20rebounding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20not%20back%20to%20where%20you%20were%2C%26quot%3B%20McKibbin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20capital%20stock%20would%20feel%20the%20impact%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20full%20recovery%20could%20take%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump's%20specific%20ideas%20about%20the%20Fed%20remain%20murky%2C%20some%20of%20his%20allies%20are%20quietly%20drafting%20plans%20on%20how%20to%20strip%20the%20central%20bank%20of%20independence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Feconomy%2Fcentral-banking%2Ftrump-allies-federal-reserve-independence-54423c2f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%2010-page%20manifesto%20apparently%20includes%20policy%20shifts%20and%20suggests%20the%20president%20should%20have%20a%20direct%20say%20over%20interest%20rates.%20Sources%20told%20the%20Journal%20the%20group%20thinks%20Trump%20should%20be%20able%20to%20fire%20Jerome%20Powell%20as%20Fed%20chair%20before%20his%20term%20ends%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20hasn't%20publicly%20acknowledged%20the%20plans%20and%20his%20advisors%20said%20they're%20not%20endorsed%20by%20the%20campaign.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKibbin%20and%20his%20fellow%20researchers%20did%20not%20examine%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris'%20policies%20in%20the%20same%20way%20because%2C%20according%20to%20the%20paper%2C%20she%20has%20not%20%26quot%3Bproposed%20any%20major%20departures%20from%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20policies%20and%20none%20with%20as%20significant%20international%20economic%20implications%20as%20Trump's.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20McKibbin%20said%20he%20wishes%20there%20was%20more%20research%20on%