essinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fwill-mortgage-rates-go-down-this-year%5C%22%3Emortgage%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20go%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%2C%20you%20might%20benefit%20from%20waiting%20to%20refinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%20makes%20sense%20for%20you%20to%20refinance%20ultimately%20comes%20down%20to%20how%20much%20you'll%20pay%20to%20refinance%20and%20how%20much%20you%20can%20save%20on%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Faverage-mortgage-payment%5C%22%3Emortgage%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20save%20enough%20each%20month%20that%20you%20can%20recoup%20your%20out-of-pocket%20expenses%20relatively%20quickly%2C%20then%20refinancing%20may%20be%20worth%20it.%20You%20could%20also%20refinance%20now%20and%20then%20refinance%20again%20once%20rates%20drop%20further%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20depends%20on%20what%20makes%20sense%20for%20you%20financially.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20Do%20Mortgage%20Interest%20Rates%20Work%3F%5C%22%3EHow%20Do%20Mortgage%20Interest%20Rates%20Work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20mortgage%20interest%20rate%20is%20how%20much%20you'll%20pay%20to%20borrow%20money%20for%20a%20home%20purchase%20or%20refinance.%20Each%20month%2C%20you'll%20make%20a%20payment%20to%20pay%20back%20the%20funds%20you%20borrowed%2C%20and%20a%20portion%20of%20that%20payment%20will%20go%20toward%20paying%20the%20interest%20you%20owe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portion%20of%20your%20monthly%20payment%20that%20goes%20toward%20interest%20will%20go%20down%20over%20time%20through%20a%20process%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fmortgage-amortization-schedule%5C%22%3Eamortization%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20you%20pay%20off%20more%20of%20your%20mortgage%2C%20the%20loan%20balance%20is%20reduced%2C%20lowering%20your%20interest%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20say%20you%20get%20a%20mortgage%20of%20%24300%2C000%20with%20an%20interest%20rate%20of%206.5%25%20to%20buy%20a%20home.%20Every%20month%2C%20you'll%20pay%20about%20%241%2C896.%20On%20your%20very%20first%20mortgage%20payment%2C%20only%20%24271%20of%20that%20amount%20will%20go%20toward%20reducing%20your%20loan%20balance%2C%20while%20%241%2C625%20will%20be%20paid%20in%20interest.%20But%20if%20you%20fast%20foward%2020%20years%2C%20%24992%20of%20that%20same%20monthly%20payment%20will%20be%20applied%20to%20the%20loan%20balance%2C%20and%20about%20%24905%20will%20go%20toward%20interest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20ask%20your%20lender%20for%20an%20amortization%20schedule%20to%20see%20the%20breakdown%20of%20your%20payments%20throughout%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan%2C%20or%20you%20can%20use%20an%20online%20amortization%20calculator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20Often%20Do%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Change%3F%5C%22%3EHow%20Often%20Do%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Change%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20change%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20and%20they%20can%20fluctuate%20day-to-day%20or%20week-to-week%20based%20on%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20economy.%20If%20economic%20conditions%20are%20relatively%20stable%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20might%20not%20move%20much.%20But%20uncertainty%20or%20expectations%20that%20conditions%20will%20change%20soon%20can%20send%20rates%20up%20or%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20Shop%20for%20Mortgage%20Rates%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Shop%20for%20Mortgage%20Rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%3EMortgage%20lenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20all%20offer%20the%20exact%20same%20rates%2C%20so%20you%20could%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20by%20shopping%20around%20for%20the%20best%20rate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20generally%20recommend%20getting%20quotes%20from%20a%20few%20different%20lenders%20%E2%80%94%20consider%20applying%20with%20at%20least%20three%20lenders%20to%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20range%20of%20rates%20available%20to%20you.%20If%20you're%20still%20early%20in%20the%20process%2C%20you%20can%20apply%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fmortgage-preapproval%5C%22%3Epreapproval%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20get%20an%20estimate%20of%20your%20rate%20while%20you're%20still%20searching%20for%20homes.%20If%20you're%20under%20contract%20on%20a%20home%2C%20you%20can%20apply%20for%20regular%20approval%2C%20which%20will%20give%20you%20a%20more%20accurate%20picture%20of%20what%20you'll%20pay%20with%20a%20given%20lender.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20sure%20to%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20offer.%20If%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20lot%20in%20fees%20to%20get%20a%20lower%20rate%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20worth%20it.%20Also%20consider%20other%20benefits%20and%20features%20that%20are%20important%20to%20you%2C%20like%20if%20a%20lender%20has%20great%20customer%20service%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fdown-payment-assistance%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%20assistance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-sunday-29-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727604002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F626bffc386fa90001905cc50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-sunday-29-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20today's%20mortgage%20and%20refinance%20rates.%20After%20dropping%20for%20several%20months%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20now%20substantially%20lower%20than%20they%20were%20a%20year%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Molly%20Grace)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-ra