2C%20seemingly%20ubiquitous%2C%20and%20carefully%20typecast%20as%20personalities%20that%20viewers%20could%20relate%20to.%20Hallstrom%2C%20who%20was%20always%20stumbling%20around%20in%20her%20high%20heels%2C%20was%20presented%20as%20the%20show's%20comic%20relief%20and%20ordered%20to%20dye%20her%20blond%20hair%20red%2C%20like%20Lucille%20Ball%20and%20Carol%20Burnett.%20She%20hated%20the%20pressure.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20terrified%20every%20moment%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20screw%20up%2C%20knock%20something%20over%2C%20or%20fall%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20klutz.%20I%20wanted%20to%20appear%20graceful%20and%20poised%2C%20like%20a%20professional%20model.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221468%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Holly%20Hallstrom%20holds%20a%20price%20sign%20on%20tv%20show%20stage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2d522d17aa3c7b2b568e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20the%20heyday%20of%20TV's%20boys%20club%2C%20Holly%20Hallstrom%20decided%20to%20stand%20up%20to%20America's%20most%20popular%20game-show%20host.%3Cp%3EThe%20Price%20is%20Right%2F%20Internet%20Archive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20hair%20color%20was%20the%20least%20of%20her%20worries.%20During%20her%20two%20decades%20on%20America's%20longest-running%20and%20most%20popular%20game%20show%2C%20Hallstrom%20was%20embroiled%20in%20the%20toxic%20and%20demeaning%20workplace%20that%20Barker%20was%20accused%20of%20creating.%20Off%20camera%2C%20the%20Beauties%20say%2C%20they%20were%20routinely%20subjected%20to%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20racial%20discrimination.%20A%20male%20staffer%20groped%20them%3B%20Barker%20hit%20on%20them%20and%20belittled%20them.%20When%20they%20complained%20to%20CBS%2C%20they%20were%20ignored%20or%20threatened%20with%20dismissal.%20Defended%20by%20the%20network%2C%20Barker%20continued%20to%20deny%20any%20wrongdoing%20right%20up%20until%20his%20death%20last%20year%20at%20the%20age%20of%2099.%20%26quot%3BIt%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20show%20or%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20once%20declared%2C%20confident%20that%20his%20word%20would%20trump%20all.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20all%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20women.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Hallstrom%2C%20along%20with%20some%20of%20the%20other%20Beauties%2C%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20unthinkable%20at%20the%20time.%20In%20the%20heyday%20of%20TV's%20boys-club%20boorishness%2C%20they%20set%20out%20to%20hold%20Barker%2C%20and%20the%20television%20industry%2C%20accountable%20for%20their%20mistreatment.%20Like%20the%20women%20who%20came%20after%20them%2C%20they%20faced%20a%20brutal%20counteroffensive.%20Barker%20and%20CBS%20shamed%20them%20in%20public%2C%20fought%20them%20in%20court%2C%20and%20bound%20them%20to%20silence%20with%20nondisclosure%20agreements.%20Fragments%20of%20what%20they%20endured%20have%20been%20public%20for%20years%2C%20and%20today%20YouTube%20is%20stuffed%20with%20vintage%20clips%20of%20%26quot%3BGreasy%20Bob%26quot%3B%20being%20sleazy%20with%20female%20contestants.%20Now%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20Hallstrom%20and%20her%20colleagues%20have%20agreed%20to%20share%20the%20full%20story%20of%20what%20they%20went%20through%20behind%20the%20scenes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20they%20decided%20to%20fight%20back.%20In%20taking%20on%20Barker%2C%20they%20not%20only%20brought%20down%20America's%20most%20beloved%20game-show%20host%2C%20they%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20a%20public%20reckoning%20of%20some%20of%20TV's%20biggest%20powerhouses%2C%20including%20Matt%20Lauer%2C%20Charlie%20Rose%2C%20Roger%20Ailes%2C%20and%20Leslie%20Moonves%2C%20who%20served%20as%20CEO%20of%20CBS%20Television%20during%20Barker's%20reign.%20Together%2C%20the%20women%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%20created%20the%20template%20for%20the%20era%20of%20%23MeToo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20came%20at%20a%20steep%20price.%20Stranded%20on%20a%20California%20road%20in%20October%202005%2C%20Hallstrom%20had%20nothing%20left%20but%20the%20scattered%20belongings%20in%20the%20car%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20envelope%20from%20CBS%20that%20was%20about%20to%20change%20everything.%20All%20she%20had%20to%20do%2C%20with%20the%20Honda's%20gas%20gauge%20stuck%20on%20empty%2C%20was%20get%20down%20the%20hill%20and%20into%20town.%20Determined%20to%20finish%20what%20she%20started%2C%20she%20shifted%20her%20car%20into%20neutral%2C%20clutched%20the%20steering%20wheel%2C%20and%20let%20it%20roll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20bright%20morning%20in%20May%20when%20we%20meet%20at%20her%20home%20near%20San%20Diego%20for%20her%20first%20interview%20in%20decades%2C%20Hallstrom%20recalls%20the%20mixture%20of%20terror%20and%20excitement%20she%20felt%20on%20that%20final%20downhill%20stretch%20of%20her%20long%20uphill%20battle.%20Now%2072%2C%20wearing%20a%20red%20flannel%20shirt%20and%20matching%20headscarf%2C%20she%20comes%20across%20as%20less%20a%20feminist%20crusader%20than%20a%20hippie%20aunt.%20Even%20though%20she%20has%20decided%20to%20break%20decades%20of%20silence%20to%20tell%20her%20story%2C%20she'd%20rather%20talk%20about%20cosmology%20or%20the%20Grateful%20Dead%20than%20revisit%20the%20trauma%20she%20endured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222593%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bob%20Barker%20sits%20as%20he%20poses%20with%20three%20of%20the%20so-called%20'Barker's%20Beauties'%20models%2C%20(left%20to%20right)%20Dian%20Parkinson%2C%20Holly%20Halstrom%2C%20and%20Janice%20Pennington.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9ea65ce3009a0fac70e4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBarker's%20Beauties%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Dian%20Parkinson%20(left)%2C%20Holly%20Hallstrom%2C%20and%20Janice%20Pennington%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0created%20the%20template%20for%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement.%20It%20came%20at%20a%20steep%20cost.%3Cp%3ECBS%20Photo%20Archive%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20happy%20to%20see%20this%20receiving%20the%20attention%20that%20is%20so%20criminally%20lacking%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20whole%20bunch%20to%20the%20story%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20what%20happened%20with%20the%20scandals%2C%20but%20the%20whole%20story%20of%20that%20time%20in%20television%20in%20America.%20But%20it's%20so%20unpleasant%20for%20me.%20It%20just%20recalls%20all%20that%20pain%20and%20anger%20and%20outrage.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20tell%20it%2C%20and%20then%20never%20talk%20about%20it%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom%20hasn't%20seen%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%20in%20ages%2C%20and%20she%20winces%20when%20I%20say%20its%20name.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20call%20it%20The%20Show%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20instructs%20me.%20Nor%20are%20we%20to%20utter%20The%20Show's%20familiar%20catchphrase%2C%20bellowed%20by%20the%20announcer%20each%20time%20a%20new%20player%20is%20beckoned%20to%20the%20stage.%20%26quot%3BNever%20say%20'come%20on%20D-O-W-N%2C'%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20says%2C%20spelling%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom%20never%20expected%20to%20come%20on%20down%20to%20the%20biggest%20game%20show%20in%20America.%20Raised%20in%20Austin%2C%20she%20grew%20up%20a%20%26quot%3Bhorrible%20little%20tomboy%20country%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20catching%20water%20moccasins%2C%20studying%20physics%2C%20and%20skipping%20a%20grade%20in%20school.%20The%20daughter%20of%20a%20Neiman%20Marcus%20model%20and%20a%20Navy%20pilot%2C%20she%20was%20on%20the%20path%20to%20becoming%20a%20Texas%20debutante%20%E2%80%94%20until%20she%20got%20thrown%20out%20of%20finishing%20school%20for%20skipping%20class.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20to%20bake%20pies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20go%20out%20and%20wrangle%20steers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom%20found%20the%20adventure%20she%20craved%20when%20her%20family%20moved%20to%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20where%20she%20became%20%26quot%3Ba%20surfing%20country%20girl%20hippie%20chick%2C%26quot%3B%20dropping%20acid%2C%20following%20the%20Dead%2C%20and%20protesting%20for%20women's%20rights.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20first%20generation%20of%20females%20to%20benefit%20from%20all%20the%20work%20and%20effort%20going%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20the%20suffragettes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20also%20knew%20I%20couldn't%20get%20a%20license%20to%20ride%20a%20motorcycle%20on%20the%20streets%20in%20California.%20I%20couldn't%20be%20in%20the%20Future%20Farmers%20of%20America.%20I%20couldn't%20take%20auto%20shop%20in%20school.%20So%20those%20were%20the%20first%20years%20that%20we%20challenged%20those%20things.%20They%20had%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22946%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Holly%20Hallstrom%20falls%20on%20the%20stage%20of%20Price%20is%20Right%20tv%20game%20show%2C%20as%20the%20hosts%20help%20her%20up.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e48186bf0250c2149350aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22732%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHallstrom%20was%20told%20to%20dye%20her%20hair%20red%20and%20play%20the%20goofball.%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Price%20is%20Right%20%2F%20Internet%20Archive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom%2C%20like%20her%20mother%2C%20was%20also%20modeling%20on%20the%20side.%20In%201976%2C%20when%20she%20was%20invited%20to%20Hollywood%20to%20try%20out%20as%20the%20new%20model%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%2C%26quot%3B%20she'd%20never%20seen%20the%20show%2C%20since%20she%20didn't%20own%20a%20TV.%20At%20her%20audition%2C%20she%20was%20instructed%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20studio%20and%20watch%20tapes%20of%20the%20show%20for%20days%20on%20end%2C%20to%20familiarize%20herself%20with%20its%20routines%20and%20cadence.%20The%20experience%20blew%20her%20mind.%20%26quot%3BIt%20looked%20just%20like%20insanity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls%20with%20a%20laugh.%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20lights%20and%20the%20bells%20and%20the%20colors%20and%20the%20screaming%20people.%20It%20looked%20like%20a%20Fellini%20movie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20orchestrated%20chaos%20was%20the%20brainchild%20of%20Mark%20Goodson%2C%20the%20co-creator%20behind%20such%20prime-time%20classics%20as%20%26quot%3BTo%20Tell%20the%20Truth%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BPassword%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20My%20Line%3F%26quot%3B%20But%20it%20was%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%20that%20proved%20the%20most%20iconic%20of%20all.%20Launched%20in%201956%20as%20the%20first%20game%20show%20for%20daytime%20TV%2C%20it%20transformed%20everyday%20American%20consumerism%20into%20mainstream%20entertainment.%20Rather%20than%20rewarding%20a%20contestant's%20knowledge%20of%20literature%20or%20history%2C%20just%20guessing%20the%20price%20of%20a%20can%20of%20beans%20could%20win%20you%20a%20dinette%20set%2C%20an%20all-expense-paid%20trip%20to%20Tahiti%2C%20or%2C%20as%20the%20slaphappy%20announcer%20Johnny%20Olson%20would%20bellow%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20NEW%20CAR!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20the%20show's%20success%20was%20Barker%2C%20who%20came%20on%20board%20in%201972.%20Lincoln%20tall%2C%20impeccably%20dressed%2C%20and%20quick-witted%2C%20Barker%20had%20mastered%20the%20improvisational%20art%20of%20hosting%20a%20live%20TV%20game%20show.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20working%20with%20civilians%2C%20and%20you%20never%20know%20what%20they're%20going%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20explains.%20Barker%20%26quot%3Bcould%20take%20whatever%20was%20thrown%20at%20him%20and%20polish%20it%2C%20respond%20with%20a%20witticism%20or%20something%20funny%20to%20rouse%20the%20audience.%20He%20was%20in%20command%20of%20that%20set.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bob%20Barker%20stands%20on%20stage%20of%20Price%20is%20right%20with%20contestant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9e4e5d17aa3c7b2b38d47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221972%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBarker%20was%20the%20key%20to%20the%20show's%20success.%20But%20backstage%2C%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20misconduct%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20towards%20the%20Beauties.%3Cp%3ECBS%20Photo%20Archive%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20in%20command%20of%20the%20show's%20trio%20of%20models.%20Janice%20Pennington%2C%20a%20former%20Playboy%20Playmate%2C%20was%20the%20veteran%20of%20the%20group%2C%20poised%20and%20refined.%20Dian%20Parkinson%2C%20a%20former%20Miss%20World%20USA%2C%20was%20hired%20to%20be%2C%20as%20she%20put%20it%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bwholesome%20sexy%26quot%3B%20one.%20Often%20clad%20in%20bikinis%20and%20negligees%2C%20she%20became%20the%20Pam%20Anderson%20of%20daytime%20TV.%20That%20left%20Hallstrom%20to%20play%20the%20goofball.%20She%20dyed%20her%20hair%20red%2C%20as%20ordered%2C%20only%20to%20watch%20it%20gradually%20devolve%20into%20a%20terrifying%20shade%20of%20pumpkin.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20do%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Lucille%20Ball%20herself%20once%20deadpanned%20to%20Hallstrom%20during%20a%20backstage%20visit.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20should%20do%20something%20about%20the%20color%20of%20your%20hair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom's%20mishaps%20and%20pratfalls%20made%20her%20a%20fan%20favorite.%20She%20bought%20a%20rambling%20house%20with%20a%20swimming%20pool%20in%20the%20hippie%20haven%20of%20Laurel%20Canyon%2C%20drove%20her%20red%20Corvette%20with%20the%20top%20down%2C%20and%20frequented%20all%20the%20hottest%20spots%2C%20from%20the%20Playboy%20mansion%20to%20Studio%2054.%20But%20the%20fame%20came%20with%20a%20price.%20One%20day%20on%20set%2C%20her%20boyfriend%20David%20Hasselhoff%2C%20the%20coiffed%20star%20of%20the%20hit%20show%20%26quot%3BKnight%20Rider%2C%26quot%3B%20stopped%20by%20with%20a%20bundle%20of%20her%20fan%20mail%20he'd%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20mailroom.%20CBS%2C%20she%20quickly%20realized%2C%20had%20been%20keeping%20some%20letters%20from%20her%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20one%20from%20a%20guy%20describing%20in%20detail%20how%20he%20was%20going%20to%20kill%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20graphic%20and%20violent%2C%20it%20was%20terrifying%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20network%20security%2C%20but%20they%20had%20no%20idea%20who%20he%20was%20or%20where%20he%20was.%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20put%20bars%20on%20her%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20wasn't%20only%20at%20home%20where%20she%20was%20beginning%20to%20feel%20uneasy.%20On%20set%2C%20she%20began%20noticing%20how%20women%20were%20being%20mistreated%20backstage.%20Not%20long%20after%20she%20was%20hired%20at%20age%2025%2C%20she%20says%2C%20Goodson%2C%20who%20was%2062%2C%20started%20coming%20on%20to%20her.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20leered%20at%20her%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20do%20you%20like%20to%20do%20when%20you're%20not%20being%20glamorous%20on%20TV%3F%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20knew%20just%20how%20to%20put%20off%20a%20stylish%20and%20well-heeled%20city%20slicker.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20him%20I%20like%20to%20go%20camping%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls%20with%20a%20laugh.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20the%20end%20of%20the%20conversation%20right%20there%2C%20because%20Mr.%20Goodson%20doesn't%20like%20to%20go%20camping.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20women%20had%20problems%20of%20their%20own.%20One%20day%2C%20when%20a%20production%20assistant%20had%20to%20stay%20home%20with%20her%20baby%20when%20her%20nanny%20called%20in%20sick%2C%20Barker%20blew%20up%20at%20her.%20She%20should%20have%20left%20the%20baby%20in%20the%20crib%2C%20he%20insisted%2C%20and%20come%20to%20work.%20Another%20time%2C%20Pennington%20was%20hit%20with%20a%20camera%20during%20a%20taping%20and%20knocked%20unconscious.%20After%20hours%20in%20surgery%2C%20she%20was%20left%20with%20a%20scar%20so%20prominent%20that%20the%20show%20stopped%20putting%20her%20in%20bikinis%20%E2%80%94%20but%20refused%20to%20cover%20her%20medical%20bills.%20Unlike%20the%20men%20in%20the%20cast%2C%20the%20Beauties%20worked%20on%20weekly%20contracts%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20they%20never%20knew%20if%20they%20had%20a%20job%20the%20following%20week%20until%20they%20received%20a%20call%20from%20a%20producer%20hiring%20them%20back.%20The%20message%2C%20Hallstrom%20says%2C%20was%20clear%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20their%20way%20of%20reminding%20you%20%E2%80%94%20you%20were%20replaceable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20late%201980s%2C%20CBS%20was%20so%20notorious%20for%20its%20lack%20of%20diversity%20that%20it%20had%20earned%20the%20nickname%20the%20Caucasian%20Broadcasting%20System.%20To%20counteract%20its%20image%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%20announced%20that%20Barker's%20Beauties%20would%20be%20adding%20a%20Black%20model.%20In%201990%2C%20after%20a%20high-profile%20nationwide%20casting%20call%2C%20Kathleen%20Bradley%2C%20a%2039-year-old%20model%20and%20singer%2C%20got%20the%20job.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20very%20proud%20to%20be%20the%20one%20that%20was%20chosen%20to%20represent%20people%20of%20color%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20dressed%20in%20jeans%20and%20a%20denim%20shirt%2C%20as%20we%20sit%20on%20the%20leafy%20patio%20of%20her%20West%20Hollywood%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20Bradley%20to%20learn%20how%20Black%20employees%20were%20treated%20on%20the%20show.%20The%20prize%20administrator%20Deborah%20Curling%2C%20one%20of%20the%20show's%20few%20other%20Black%20staffers%2C%20warned%20Bradley%20of%20the%20frequent%20racial%20slurs%20backstage.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20Bradley%20found%20that%20all%20kinds%20of%20%26quot%3Boffensive%20and%20discriminatory%20remarks%2C%20including%20those%20against%20blacks%2C%20women%2C%20gays%2C%20and%20other%20minorities%2C%20were%20tolerated%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3BBackstage%20at%20The%20Price%20Is%20Right.%26quot%3B%20Barker%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20had%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20bigot.%20When%20Black%20contestants%20tried%20to%20embrace%20him%2C%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bjokingly%26quot%3B%20run%20from%20them%2C%20as%20if%20they%20posed%20a%20threat.%20Black%20contestants%20were%20marked%20on%20the%20show's%20call%20sheet%20with%20the%20letter%20B%2C%20and%20were%20called%20only%20during%20the%20third%20act%20of%20the%20show%2C%20when%20contestants'%20row%20was%20already%20filled%20with%20whites.%20%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20want%20too%20many%2C%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kathleen%20Bradley%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f18f20d17aa3c7b2b4fd17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKathleen%20Bradley%20was%20the%20first%20to%20report%20a%20crew%20member%20notorious%20for%20groping%20the%20models.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Grayson%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESexual%20assault%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20colorblind.%20One%20crew%20member%20had%20become%20notorious%20for%20groping%20the%20Beauties%20backstage%2C%20but%20no%20one%20had%20found%20the%20courage%20to%20speak%20up.%20But%20when%20he%20tried%20it%20on%20Bradley%2C%20she%20immediately%20went%20to%20management%20and%20reported%20him.%20CBS%2C%20she%20says%2C%20ignored%20her%20complaint.%20%26quot%3BThe%20higher-ups%20never%20took%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20he%20was%20merely%20given%20a%20slap%20on%20the%20wrist%20for%20his%20bad%20behavior.%26quot%3B%20So%20Bradley%20took%20matters%20into%20her%20own%20hands.%20One%20day%2C%20while%20she%20was%20idly%20swinging%20a%20golf%20club%20from%20a%20prize%20display%2C%20she%20beckoned%20the%20crew%20member%20over%20to%20help%20her.%20When%20he%20wrapped%20his%20arms%20around%20her%20to%20show%20her%20how%20to%20swing%2C%20she%20whipped%20the%20club%20between%20his%20legs.%20%26quot%3BI%20swung%20around%20and%20hit%20him%20in%20his%20little%20peanut%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20The%20crew%20member%20stopped%20his%20groping%2C%20but%20he%20kept%20his%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20CBS%20responded%20to%20the%20complaints%20by%20imposing%20what%20became%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3B10-Second%20Rule.%26quot%3B%20No%20crew%20member%2C%20the%20network%20decreed%2C%20was%20permitted%20to%20stare%20openly%20at%20the%20Beauties%20for%20longer%20than%2010%20seconds.%20But%20no%20one%20kept%20a%20stopwatch%20on%20the%20offenders%2C%20and%20the%20ogling%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20atmosphere%20grew%20more%20toxic%20when%20it%20became%20an%20open%20secret%20that%20Parkinson%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bwholesome%20sexy%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20slipping%20in%20and%20out%20of%20Barker's%20dressing%20room.%20%26quot%3BShe'd%20put%20her%20robe%20on%20and%20go%20down%20during%20the%20breaks%2C%20then%20come%20back%20up%20with%20a%20smile%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20tell%20when%20Barker%20was%20happy%20that%20day.%20You%20could%20tell%20that%20glow.%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20says%20that%20Parkinson%20told%20her%20she%20was%20sleeping%20with%20Barker%2C%20a%2066-year-old%20widower%2C%20because%20he%20%26quot%3Bneeded%20a%20little%20hanky-panky%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20life.%20(Parkinson%20and%20Pennington%20declined%20requests%20to%20share%20their%20experiences%20for%20this%20story.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20affair%20soon%20spilled%20over%20to%20the%20show%20itself.%20During%20one%20taping%2C%20Barker%20leaned%20over%20to%20Parkinson%2C%20who%20was%20dressed%20in%20a%20revealing%20pink%20negligee.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20have%20a%20little%20chat%20with%20you%20in%20your%20nighty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20about%20time!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20going%20to%20get%20your%20clothes%20on%20before%20we%20play%20another%20price%20game%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20cooed.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I'll%20tease%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20affair%20divided%20the%20Beauties%2C%20who%20felt%20that%20Barker%20was%20favoring%20Parkinson.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20exactly%20how%20we%20knew%20when%20she%20started%20having%20sex%20with%20Barker%2C%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20says.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20here%20come%20the%20producers%20all%20suddenly%20kissing%20Dian's%20ass%20like%20she%20might%20be%20the%20new%20Mrs.%20Barker.%26quot%3B%20At%20Barker's%20insistence%2C%20Parkinson%20was%20even%20allowed%20to%20pose%20for%20the%20cover%20of%20Playboy%2C%20over%20Goodson's%20objections.%20Backstage%2C%20the%20Beauties%20began%20bickering%20among%20themselves.%20Barker%2C%20frustrated%20by%20the%20increasingly%20hostile%20work%20environment%20he%20had%20created%2C%20lashed%20out%20at%20those%20around%20him.%20%26quot%3BMy%20life%20for%20five%20years%20became%20hell%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20recalls%20Linda%20Riegert%2C%20a%20production%20assistant.%20During%20one%20commercial%20break%2C%20after%20she%20made%20a%20mistake%20placing%20a%20prop%2C%20he%20called%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bstupid%20bitch.%26quot%3B%20Riegert%20began%20getting%20migraines%20and%20sobbing%20in%20her%20dressing%20room%20after%20tapings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bikini%20cover%20of%20Playboy%20with%20Dian%20Parkinson.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e48feecfb7f307e5718824%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EParkinson%2C%20at%20Barker's%20insistence%2C%20was%20permitted%20to%20pose%20for%20the%20cover%20of%20Playboy.%3Cp%3EDian%20Parkinson%2F%20PlayBoy%20Magazine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBarker%20called%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Beauties%20and%20blamed%20them%20for%20the%20tensions.%20%26quot%3BLadies%2C%20we%20cannot%20afford%20to%20continue%20to%20have%20this%20kind%20of%20discord%20behind%20the%20scenes%20on%20this%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20them.%20%26quot%3BPlease%2C%20try%20to%20work%20out%20your%20differences%20and%20make%20peace.%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20got%20a%20note%20from%20Goodson%20accusing%20her%20of%20spreading%20rumors%20about%20Parkinson.%20If%20she%20didn't%20%26quot%3Bstraighten%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned%20her%2C%20she%20was%20going%20to%20be%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlindsided%2C%20Hallstrom%20called%20Goodson's%20office%20and%20demanded%20to%20meet%20with%20him.%20In%20person%2C%20she%20says%2C%20he%20confessed%20that%20Barker%20and%20Parkinson%20were%20the%20ones%20behind%20the%20threat.%20%26quot%3BListen%2C%26quot%3B%20Goodson%20told%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20Barker%20is%20sleeping%20with%20Dian.%20I%20know%20Dian%20hates%20you%20with%20a%20passion.%20And%20she%20is%20filling%20his%20head%20during%20the%20pillow%20talk.%26quot%3B%20There%20was%20nothing%2C%20he%20added%2C%20that%20he%20could%20do%20to%20help%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20no%20longer%20control%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBarker%20seized%20control%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom%20heard%20the%20same%20thing%20from%20a%20surprising%20source%3A%20Nancy%20Burnet%2C%20Barker's%20girlfriend%20at%20the%20time.%20One%20day%2C%20Burnet%20called%20Hallstrom%20out%20of%20the%20blue%20to%20warn%20her%20that%20she%20had%20overheard%20Barker%20calling%20Goodson.%20%26quot%3BIf%20one%20more%20thing%20happens%20on%20that%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20Barker%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3Bfire%20Holly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tensions%20worsened%20when%20Barker%20learned%20that%20Parkinson%20had%20been%20sleeping%20with%20Black%20men%2C%20including%20the%20singer%20Smokey%20Robinson%20and%20the%20actor%20Tim%20Reid.%20%26quot%3BHe%20went%20through%20the%20roof%2C%26quot%3B%20Parkinson%20confided%20to%20Bradley.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20heard%20him%20that%20upset%20and%20nasty.%26quot%3B%20When%20Bradley%20asked%20why%20Barker%20was%20so%20angry%2C%20Parkinson%20didn't%20mince%20words%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20always%20had%20the%20idea%20that%20if%20he%20was%20involved%20with%20someone%20who'd%20had%20sexual%20relations%20with%20a%20Black%20man%2C%20he%20might%20contract%20some%20sort%20of%20communicable%20disease%20just%20because%20they're%20Black.%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20heard%20a%20similar%20account%20from%20Burnet%2C%20who%20told%20her%2C%20%26quot%3BBarker%20says%20Black%20men%20are%20the%20most%20diseased%20creatures%20on%20earth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20breaking%20point%20came%20when%20Barker%20learned%20that%20Parkinson%20was%20planning%20to%20do%20a%20second%20photo%20shoot%20with%20Playboy%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20fully%20nude.%20He%20called%20Parkinson%20into%20his%20dressing%20room%20where%20they%20had%20what%20Hallstrom%20recalls%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20huge%20screaming%20fight.%26quot%3B%20When%20Parkinson%20stormed%20out%20in%20a%20huff%2C%20one%20of%20Barker's%20assistants%20chased%20after%20her%20and%20pleaded%20with%20her%20to%20patch%20things%20up.%20%26quot%3BYou%20gotta%20go%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20assistant%20pleaded.%20%26quot%3BYou%20gotta%20apologize.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Hallstrom%20recalls%20the%20moment%2C%20Parkinson%20was%20standing%20on%20a%20stairway%20outside%20the%20dressing%20rooms%2C%20where%20everyone%20backstage%20could%20see%20her.%20As%20they%20all%20looked%20on%2C%20she%20drew%20herself%20up%20and%20refused%20to%20back%20down.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20sucked%20his%20dick%20too%20many%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20start%20kissing%20his%20ass%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAwestruck%2C%20one%20of%20the%20writers%20turned%20to%20Hallstrom.%20%26quot%3BWho%20writes%20for%20her%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June