20with%20him%20only%20because%20she%20feared%20losing%20her%20job%20if%20she%20declined.%20Now%20she%20wanted%20%248%20million%20for%20her%20pain%20and%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20probably%20going%20to%20get%20called%20in%20for%20depositions%2C%26quot%3B%20Barker%20told%20the%20women.%20%26quot%3BJust%20go%20in%20there%20and%20tell%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20were%20skeptical.%20They'd%20been%20complaining%20for%20years%20about%20the%20hostile%20workplace%2C%20the%20sexism%2C%20the%20disharmony%2C%20and%20not%20once%20had%20Barker%20taken%20any%20responsibility.%20But%20now%20that%20he%20was%20faced%20with%20a%20scandal%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20know%20they%20had%20his%20back.%20%26quot%3BOK%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20you%20want%20to%20schmooze%20up%20to%20your%20Beauties%20again%20now%20that%20it%20suits%20your%20personal%20needs%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cover%20of%20magazine%2C%20National%20Enquirer%20dated%20July%2019th%2C%201994.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e89bfdcfb7f307e5722218%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22995%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAllegations%20of%20Barker's%20misconduct%20made%20the%20cover%20of%20tabloids%20like%20the%20National%20Enquirer.%20%3Cp%3ENational%20Enquirer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2027%2C%201994%2C%20Barker%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20and%20denounced%20Parkinson%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms.%20Barker%20blamed%20her%20for%20the%20affair.%20%26quot%3BShe%20told%20me%20that%20I%20had%20been%20so%20straitlaced%20and%20that%20it%20was%20time%20I%20had%20a%20little%20hanky-panky%20in%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20she%20volunteered%20the%20hanky-panky.%26quot%3B%20He%20denied%20the%20harassment.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20case%20of%20two%20middle-aged%20adults%2C%20consenting%20adults%2C%20having%20sex%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20went%20on.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20as%20simple%20as%20that.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20headline%2C%20a%20tabloid%20captured%20what%20it%20saw%20as%20the%20gist%20of%20Barker's%20defense%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20old%20man%20is%20innocent%2C%20guys!%20Don't%20listen%20to%20that%20mixed-up%20bimbo.%20She's%20mad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20proved%20relatively%20simple%20to%20push%20Parkinson%20aside.%20She%20ended%20up%20dropping%20the%20suit%2C%20saying%20she%20couldn't%20compete%20with%20the%20deep%20pockets%20she%20was%20up%20against.%20%26quot%3BBob%20Barker%20has%20beaten%20me%20into%20submission%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20doctor%20has%20advised%20that%20I%20am%20not%20strong%20enough%20to%20see%20this%20thing%20through.%20As%20a%20single%20woman%2C%20I%20was%20no%20match%20for%20the%20power%20and%20resources%20of%20Bob%20Barker%20and%20Goodson%20Productions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Beauty%20had%20fallen.%20As%20Hallstrom%20soon%20learned%2C%20Parkinson%20would%20not%20be%20the%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20mounting%20dissent%2C%20Barker%20kept%20the%20show%20a%20hit.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20always%20focused%20on%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20Roger%20Neal%2C%20his%20longtime%20publicist%2C%20tells%20me.%20We're%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20life-size%20cutout%20of%20Barker%20smiling%20at%20visitors%20inside%20the%20Hollywood%20Museum%2C%20a%20kitschy%20tourist%20attraction%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20%26quot%3BHe%20always%20focused%20on%20the%20animals%2C%26quot%3B%20Neal%20says%2C%20noting%20Barker's%20years%20as%20an%20animal-rights%20crusader.%20%26quot%3BAlways%20focused%20on%20the%20fans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20display%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20legendary%20status%20Barker%20still%20maintains.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%20remains%20the%20second-highest-rated%20show%20for%20CBS%2C%20and%20it%20continues%20to%20rank%20among%20the%2010%20most%20watched%20shows%20on%20TV.%20And%20thanks%20to%20the%20classic-game-show%20channel%20Buzzr%2C%20Barker%20is%20now%20back%20on%20the%20air%20with%20daily%20reruns.%20TikTok%20revels%20in%20kitschy%20Barker-era%20memes%2C%20and%20even%20in%20the%20age%20of%20%23MeToo%2C%20the%20glowing%20obituaries%20that%20followed%20his%20death%20made%20scant%20mention%20of%20his%20on-set%20behavior.%20As%20the%20game-show%20historian%20and%20author%20Adam%20Nedeff%20says%2C%20the%20franchise%20Barker%20built%20continues%20to%20deliver%20%26quot%3Bmultigenerational%20comfort%20food%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20nation%20hungry%20for%20nostalgia%20and%20distraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fans%20cheer%20from%20the%20stands%20of%20Price%20is%20Right%20Game%20show.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9de8dcfb7f307e5727a68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221928%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBarker%20created%20a%20franchise%20that%20one%20historian%20calls%20%26quot%3Bmultigenerational%20comfort%20food.%26quot%3B%20Today%20it%20continues%20to%20rank%20among%20the%2010%20most%20watched%20shows%20on%20television.%3Cp%3EM.%20Phillips%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20backstage%2C%20Barker%20was%20furious%20at%20Hallstrom%20for%20her%20refusal%20to%20toe%20the%20line.%20%26quot%3BBarker%20was%20not%20real%20happy%20with%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20resentful%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20back%20him%20up.%26quot%3B%20While%20Barker%20made%20the%20media%20rounds%20denouncing%20Parkinson%2C%20Hallstrom%2C%20Pennington%2C%20and%20Bradley%20were%20booked%20to%20appear%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Suzanne%20Somers%20Show.%26quot%3B%20When%20pressed%20on%20Parkinson's%20claims%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20Hallstrom%20deflected.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20present%20for%20any%20conversation%20regarding%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20But%20now%20she%20tells%20me%20what%20she%20wished%20she%20could%20have%20said%20back%20then.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20Dian%20was%20not%20lying%20about%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20Hallstrom%20refused%20to%20trash%20Parkinson%20in%20court%20and%20in%20the%20press%2C%20the%20more%20outraged%20Barker%20became.%20One%20day%2C%20he%20told%20her%20to%20provide%20a%20list%20of%20Parkinson's%20boyfriends%20to%20a%20tabloid%20reporter.%20When%20she%20refused%2C%20Barker%20blew%20up.%20That%2C%20she%20later%20testified%2C%20was%20when%20he%20began%20focusing%20on%20her%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarker%20had%20always%20badgered%20the%20Beauties%20about%20their%20weight%2C%20routinely%20popping%20into%20their%20dressing%20room%20whenever%20he%20thought%20one%20of%20them%20looked%20too%20heavy.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20allow%20one%20or%20two%20pounds%20to%20slide%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20would%20tell%20them%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20will%20generally%20be%20more%20pounds%20to%20follow.%20So%20weigh%20yourself%20daily.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Hallstrom%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20a%20hormonal%20imbalance%20caused%20by%20a%20hysterectomy%20she'd%20had%20for%20ovarian%20cysts.%20The%20prescription%20estrogen%20and%20progesterone%20she%20was%20taking%20came%20with%20a%20side%20effect%3A%20weight%20gain.%20She%20explained%20the%20difficulties%20of%20her%20condition%20to%20Barker%20and%20asked%20for%20some%20additional%20time%20to%20lose%20weight%20during%20the%20show's%20coming%20hiatus.%20The%20request%20was%20denied.%20When%20a%20top%20executive%20at%20Barker's%20production%20company%20visited%20the%20set%2C%20he%20eyed%20Hallstrom%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20are%20you%20doing%2C%20Pillsbury%20Dough%20Girl%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20night%20after%20work%2C%20Barker%20and%20the%20producer%20Roger%20Dobkowitz%20returned%20to%20Hallstrom's%20dressing%20room%20to%20discuss%20her%20weight.%20Bradley%20was%20also%20present%2C%20and%20Riegert%20overheard%20the%20talk%20from%20her%20own%20dressing%20room.%20When%20Barker%20ordered%20Hallstrom%20to%20lose%20the%20weight%20in%20a%20week%2C%20she%20protested.%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20I%20can%20lose%20the%20weight%20is%20to%20go%20off%20my%20medication%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20him.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20want%20me%20to%20go%20off%20of%20my%20medication%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20lose%20the%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Holly%20Hallstrom%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20a%20product%20while%20wearing%20a%20bikini.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9e10fcfb7f307e5727c39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHallstrom%20on%20set%20in%201994%2C%20around%20the%20time%20Barker%20demanded%20she%20lose%20weight.%3Cp%3EThe%20Price%20is%20Right%20%2F%20Internet%20Archive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFearing%20for%20her%20job%2C%20Hallstrom%20gave%20in.%20%26quot%3BI%20went%20off%20my%20medication%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20later%20testified.%20But%20Barker%20wasn't%20through%20with%20her.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Jonathan%20Goodson%2C%20who%20had%20taken%20over%20the%20production%20company%20from%20his%20father%2C%20called%20a%20meeting%20and%20fat-shamed%20Hallstrom%20in%20front%20of%20the%20entire%20cast%20and%20crew%2C%20according%20to%20four%20people%20who%20were%20present.%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20Mr.%20Barker%20wants%20us%20to%20help%20Holly%20lose%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20recall%20Goodson%20saying.%20Until%20she%20did%2C%20he%20went%20on%2C%20she%20would%20be%20granted%20no%20close-ups%2C%20and%20would%20not%20appear%20until%20the%20third%20act%20of%20the%20show.%20Whenever%20she%20was%20on%20camera%2C%20she%20would%20be%20positioned%20behind%20the%20prizes%2C%20so%20no%20one%20could%20see%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20ask%20Hallstrom%20how%20she%20felt%20in%20that%20moment%2C%20she%20falls%20silent%20for%20a%20long%20beat%20as%20her%20eyes%20well.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20the%20rabbit%20who%20looks%20up%20just%20in%20time%20to%20see%20the%20face%20of%20the%20viper%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BThat%20horrible%20feeling%20inside.%20Wow.%20Intense.%20When%20your%20guts%20just%20turn%20to%20liquid.%26quot%3B%20Sure%20enough%2C%20starting%20with%20that%20day's%20taping%2C%20she%20disappeared%20from%20view.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20hidden%20behind%20cars%20and%20boats%20and%20refrigerators%20and%20stuff%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Everyone%20knew%20what%20was%20happening.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20mistreating%20her%20on%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20says.%20%26quot%3BYou%20could%20tell%20she%20was%20just%20getting%20eased%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20week%20later%2C%20Barker%20confronted%20Hallstrom%20in%20her%20dressing%20room.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20furious%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20screaming%20at%20me.%26quot%3B%20In%20fear%20of%20a%20lawsuit%2C%20he%20denied%20having%20told%20her%20to%20go%20off%20her%20meds.%20She%20refused%20to%20back%20down%2C%20and%20that%20was%20that.%20On%20October%2027%2C%201995%2C%20her%20last%20appearance%20aired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Parkinson%20before%20her%2C%20Hallstrom%20went%20public%20with%20the%20reasons%20for%20her%20firing.%20The%20reason%20Barker%20pushed%20her%20out%2C%20she%20told%20the%20press%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20I%20was%20not%20cooperating%20with%20his%20publicity%20campaign%20to%20smear%20Dian%20when%20she%20filed%20a%20suit%20against%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarker%20took%20to%20the%20air%20to%20launch%20a%20PR%20campaign%20against%20her.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20company%20were%20going%20to%20terminate%20her%20for%20a%20weight%20problem%2C%20Holly%20would%20have%20been%20gone%20years%20and%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%26quot%3BEntertainment%20Tonight.%26quot%3B%20Another%20time%2C%20he%20said%20her%20weight%20had%20fluctuated%20so%20much%20that%20for%20a%20while%20she%20%26quot%3Bwas%20wearing%20a%20full%20body%20girdle%20down%20to%20her%20thighs.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom's%20lawyers%20urged%20her%20to%20sue%20Barker%20for%20libel%20and%20medical%20discrimination%2C%20but%20she%20refused%20to%20play%20that%20game%20for%20one%20reason%3A%20She%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20muzzled%20by%20a%20nondisclosure%20agreement%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20CBS%20settled%20for.%20Instead%2C%20she%20would%20simply%20sit%20back%20and%20wait%20for%20Barker%20to%20sue%20her%20first.%20That%20way%20she%20could%20countersue%20him%2C%20winning%20a%20victory%20without%20having%20to%20sign%20an%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20telling%20you%2C%20this%20man%20is%20stupid%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20her%20lawyers.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20going%20to%20sue%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom%20was%20betting%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20that%20Barker's%20ego%20would%20get%20the%20better%20of%20him.%20She%20and%20others%20think%20that%20Barker%2C%20on%20some%20level%2C%20actually%20relished%20his%20bouts%20with%20Parkinson%2C%20which%20cast%20him%20as%20a%20virile%20older%20man%20with%20a%20young%20sexpot%20girlfriend.%20%26quot%3BHe%20wanted%20that%20big%20old%20celebration%20of%20Bob%2C%20the%20silver-haired%20stud%2C%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20says.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%3A%20Here's%20another%20model%20suing%20him.%26quot%3B%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%20for%20Barker%2C%20fans%20began%20to%20miss%20their%20favorite%20Beauty.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20he%20would%20sue%20me%20because%20he%20couldn't%20take%20the%20hit%20to%20his%20ego%20that%20suddenly%20the%20fans%20were%20turning%20against%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gamble%20paid%20off.%20Within%20days%2C%20Barker%20sued%20her%2C%20alleging%20defamation%20of%20character.%20Hallstrom%2C%20as%20planned%2C%20countersued%20with%20her%20own%20defamation%20claim%20as%20well%20as%20allegations%20of%20infliction%20of%20emotional%20distress%20and%20discrimination%20based%20on%20disability%2C%20age%2C%20and%20sex.%20The%20legal%20battle%20raged%20for%20years%2C%20draining%20Hallstrom's%20hope%20and%20bank%20account.%20Having%20spoken%20out%2C%20she%20was%20viewed%20as%20radioactive%20by%20the%20industry.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20was%20returning%20my%20calls%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20But%20even%20when%20she%20was%20offered%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20to%20settle%2C%20she%20turned%20the%20deals%20down%2C%20refusing%20to%20be%20silenced%20by%20an%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Janice%20Pennington%20sitting%20on%20a%20patio%20chair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e89ae5d17aa3c7b2b32e89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221143%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJanice%20Pennington%20was%20fired%20in%202000%20after%20she%20and%20Bradley%20testified%20in%20support%20of%20Hallstrom.%3Cp%3EAnnie%20Wells%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20remaining%20Beauties%2C%20Bradley%20and%20Pennington%2C%20made%20a%20different%20decision.%20In%20September%202000%2C%20after%20returning%20to%20the%20show%20from%20the%20summer%20hiatus%2C%20they%20each%20got%20subpoenaed%20to%20testify%20on%20Barker's%20behalf%20against%20Hallstrom.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Barker%20called%20them%20to%20his%20office%2C%20flanked%20by%20the%20show's%20director%20and%20producer.%20When%20Barker%20pressed%20Bradley%20to%20reveal%20the%20contents%20of%20her%20deposition%2C%20she%20told%20the%20truth.%20%26quot%3BI%20distinctly%20recall%20you%20not%20telling%20Holly%20to%20stop%20taking%20her%20medication%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20for%20her%20to%20do%20whatever%20was%20necessary%20to%20lose%20the%20weight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarker%20glared%20at%20her.%20%26quot%3BEither%20you're%20lying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bor%20you're%20making%20it%20up.%26quot%3B%20She%20wasn't%2C%20and%20she%20had%20the%20proof%20%E2%80%94%20a%20diary%20of%20everything%20that%20had%20happened%2C%20including%20dates%20and%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20both%20she%20and%20Pennington%20were%20fired.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20a%20dagger%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20believe%20it%20%E2%80%94%20my%20whole%20head%20spaced%20out.%26quot%3B%20She%20stumbled%20to%20her%20car%2C%20where%20she%20broke%20down%20in%20tears%2C%20furious%20at%20being%20kicked%20to%20the%20curb%20for%20telling%20the%20truth.%20But%20rather%20than%20risk%20the%20costly%20and%20time-consuming%20campaign%20required%20to%20take%20on%20CBS%2C%20Bradley%20and%20Pennington%20settled%20out%20of%20court%2C%20agreeing%20to%20sign%20NDAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20weren't%20the%20only%20women%20fired%20for%20refusing%20to%20play%20Barker's%20game.%20The%20same%20day%2C%20Linda%20Riegert%20and%20Sherrell%20Paris%2C%20Barker's%20executive%20assistant%20of%2023%20years%2C%20were%20also%20fired%20for%20refusing%20to%20back%20up%20Barker.%20Both%20women%20sued%20for%20wrongful%20termination%2C%20saying%20they'd%20been%20fired%20in%20retaliation%20for%20testifying%20against%20Barker.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20the%20truth%20about%20what%20went%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Riegert%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiegert's%20case%20was%20dismissed%20because%20she%20had%20signed%20an%20arbitration%20agreement%20when%20she%20was%20fired%2C%20and%20Paris%20settled%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20amount.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBut%20Hallstrom%20continued%20to%20hold%20out.%20Being%20single%20and%20childless%2C%20she%20says%2C%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20her%20to%20bet%20everything%20she%20had.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20a%20unique%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20the%20one%20who%20could%20stand%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202004%2C%20Hallstrom%20had%20lost%20all%20her%20money%2C%20and%20was%20forced%20to%20sell%20her%20home.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShe%20was%20sleeping%20in%20a%20shed%20and%20living%20out%20of%20her%20car.%20She%20would%20have%20used%20the%20car%20to%20kill%20herself%2C%20she%20tells%20me%2C%20but%20she%20had%20nowhere%20to%20park%20inside.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20have%20gotten%20the%20car%20in%20the%20garage%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20be%20standing%20here%20today.%26quot%3B%20But%20something%20inside%20her%20kept%20her%20going.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20know%20what%20was%20going%20to%20happen%20or%20how%20it%20was%20going%20to%20unfold%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20just%20knew%20it%20was%20not%20going%20to%20go%20the%20way%20they%20thought%20it%20was%20going%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20before%20her%20case%20was%20scheduled%20to%20go%20to%20trial%2C%20her%20lawyer%20contacted%20her%20with%20urgent%20news.%20Barker%20and%20CBS%20were%20settling.%20The%20network%20agreed%20to%20pay%20her%20what%20she%20will%20only%20say%20was%20several%20million%20dollars.%20And%20with%20it%20came%20an%20even%20bigger%20victory%3A%20She%20would%20not%20have%20to%20sign%20an%20NDA.%20Despite%20years%20of%20intimidation%2C%20she%20was%20free%20to%20tell%20her%20truth%20whenever%20she%20wanted.%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20dropping%20to%20my%20knees%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20true%20%E2%80%94%20that%20happens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDown%20to%20her%20last%2048%20cents%2C%20Hallstrom%20scrounged%20her%20sofa%20cushions%20for%20enough%20change%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20gallon%20of%20gas%20to%20get%20her%20to%20the%20bank%20and%20deposit%20the%20check.%20But%20she%20ran%20out%20of%20gas%20before%20she%20made%20it%2C%20and%20had%20to%20roll%20down%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20road%20in%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BToday%26quot%3B%20show%2C%20she%20was%20asked%20why%20she%20had%20continued%20her%20fight%20even%20after%20she%20was%20homeless.%20Hallstrom%20remained%20unequivocal.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20you%20cannot%20be%20forced%20to%20do%20anything%20illegal%2C%20such%20as%20lie%20for%20your%20boss%2C%20or%20suffer%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20racial%20discrimination%20or%20discrimination%20of%20any%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20we%20have%20rights%2C%20and%20they%20have%20recourse.%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20sold%20her%20beat-up%20Honda%20and%20bought%20herself%20a%20roomier%20ride%20from%20which%20to%20live%3A%20a%20luxury%20tour%20bus.%20Packing%20her%20things%2C%20she%20hit%20the%20road%20for%20the%20Pacific%20Northwest%2C%20far%20from%20the%20Hollywood%20she%20forever%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20she%20paved%20would%20soon%20lead%20to%20the%20final%20prize.%20Eighteen%20months%20later%2C%20in%20April%202007%2C%20the%20longtime%20%26quot%3BPrice%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%20employee%20Deborah%20Curling%2C%20the%20woman%20who%20had%20first%20warned%20Bradley%20about%20racism%20on%20the%20set%20in%201990%2C%20sued%20Barker%20and%20CBS%20with%20claims%20of%20wrongful%20termination%20and%20a%20hostile%20work%20environment.%20Barker%2C%20her%20lawsuit%20alleged%2C%20%26quot%3Bintentionally%20inflicted%20emotional%20distress%20on%20Curling%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20racist%20and%20antisemitic%20jokes.%26quot%3BAny%20employee%20who%20complained%20about%20the%20working%20environment%20or%20contradicted%20Barker%20was%20fired%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20named%20more%20than%20Barker%20in%20the%20suit.%20Eleven%20years%20before%20the%20CBS%20chair%20and%20CEO%20Les%20Moonves%20would%20be%20brought%20down%20for%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20sexual%20assault%2C%20Curling%20sought%20to%20depose%20him%20over%20his%20own%20%26quot%3Bconduct%2C%20which%20constitutes%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20creates%20a%20hostile%20working%20environment.%26quot%3B%20She%20warned%20that%20he%20and%20other%20executives%20had%20created%20%26quot%3Ba%20widespread%20policy%20of%20sexual%20favoritism%20that%20is%20set%20from%20the%20top%20at%20CBS.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20judge%20refused%20to%20allow%20Curling%20to%20depose%20Moonves%2C%20and%20eventually%20granted%20a%20summary%20judgment%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20network%20and%20Barker.%20But%20CBS%20had%20apparently%20had%20enough.%20Barker's%20game%20was%20over.%20In%20June%202007%2C%20he%20taped%20his%20last%20show%2C%20telling%20the%20audience%20he%20had%20decided%20to%20retire.%20While%20he%20didn't%20mention%20the%20claims%20against%20him%20over%20all%20the%20years%2C%20he%20did%20let%20on%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20go%20wasn't%20entirely%20his%20own.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20not%20ready%20to%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%2083%2C%20so%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20good%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20on%20down!%20You're%20the%20next%20contestant%20on%20'The%20Price%20Is%20Right'!%26quot%3B%20The%20show's%20current%20announcer%2C%20George%20Gray%2C%20is%20bellowing%20the%20familiar%20catchphrase%20during%20a%20taping%20of%20the%20show%20in%20Glendale%2C%20California.%20Inside%20the%20blindingly%20bright%2C%20candy-colored%20studio%2C%20the%20slaphappy%20audience%20parties%20like%20it's%201979%2C%20shouting%20and%20dancing%20in%20the%20aisles.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20my%20first%20plane%20trip%20to%20get%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Mary%20Capps%2C%20a%20grandmother%20who%20arrived%20with%20her%20family%20in%20matching%20T-shirts%2C%20tells%20me%20before%20the%20show.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20use%20a%20barf%20bag!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%20remains%20the%20top-rated%20game%20show%20on%20TV%2C%20the%20troubles%20of%20the%20Barker%20era%20didn't%20end%20with%20his%20departure.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20in%20March%202010%2C%20the%20model%20Brandi%20Cochran%20sued%20the%20show%20and%20CBS%2C%20claiming%20she%20was%20ridiculed%20about%20her%20weight%20and%20barred%20from%20returning%20to%20work%20after%20taking%20maternity%20leave.%20A%20jury%20awarded%20her%20%248.5%20million%20in%20damages%2C%20but%20the%20verdict%20was%20overturned%20because%20of%20an%20error%20by%20the%20judge.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20the%20model%20Lanisha%20Cole%20sued%20the%20show%20for%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20alleging%20that%20a%20producer%20had%20barged%20into%20her%20dressing%20room%20when%20she%20was%20naked.%20CBS%20settled%20with%20both%20Cole%20and%20Cochran%20for%20undisclosed%20sums.%20Thanks%20to%20Hallstrom%20and%20the%20other%20Beauties%2C%20women%20on%20the%20show%20now%20had%20a%20model%20for%20how%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20and%20hold%20the%20network%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%2C%20from%20left%20to%20right%3A%20%20Janice%20Pennington%2C%20Kathleen%20Bradley%2C%20Holly%20Hallstrom%20and%20Dian%20Parkinson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2e107ce3009a0fac8ea23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221061%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20women%20(from%20left)%20who%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20%23MeToo%3A%20Pennington%2C%20Bradley%2C%20Hallstrom%2C%20and%20Parkinson.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Livingston%3B%20Victoria%20Sirakova%3B%20Ron%20Galella%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom%20has%20advice%20for%20anyone%20considering%20speaking%20up%20at%20work.%20%26quot%3BDo%20everything%20you%20can%20to%20maintain%20your%20personal%20power%20and%20your%20ethics%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you%20are%20brave%20enough%20and%20can%20support%20yourself%20and%20whoever%20you%20need%20to%20support%20through%20a%20long%20battle%2C%20then%20by%20all%20means%20stand%20up%2C%20speak%20out%2C%20and%20resist.%20Because%20the%20women%20I%20know%20who%20did%20not%2C%20it%20stains%20your%20soul%2C%20and%20it%20never%20goes%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20women%20who%20took%20on%20Barker%20during%20his%20heyday%2C%20the%20nightmare%20of%20their%20time%20on%20the%20show%20continues%20to%20haunt%20them.%20Riegert%2C%20Barker's%20longtime%20assistant%2C%20still%20suffers%20from%20what%20the%20women%20jokingly%20call%20%26quot%3BPricemares%26quot%3B%20about%20their%20time%20on%20the%20set.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20usually%20about%20Barker%20coming%20at%20you%20with%20his%20mic%2C%20shaking%20it%20at%20you%2C%20or%20him%20looking%20at%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Riegert%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20ever%20saw%20the%20meanest%20look%20ever%20on%20somebody's%20face%2C%20you%20never%2C%20ever%20forget%20it.%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20has%20Pricemares%20in%20which%20Parkinson%20is%20storming%20across%20the%20stage%20in%20a%20murderous%20rage.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20mad%20at%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20says.%20%26quot%3BShe%20wanted%20to%20kill%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHallstrom%20still%20gets%20the%20occasional%20Pricemare%2C%20too.%20Sometimes%20they%20mirror%20the%20struggle%20she%20and%20so%20many%20other%20women%20continue%20to%20face%20in%20the%20workplace%3A%20She%20can't%20figure%20out%20what%20is%20expected%20of%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20had%20one%20where%20it's%20like%3A%20Oh%20my%20gosh%2C%20where%20am%20I%20supposed%20to%20be%3F%20Door%20three%3F%20Door%20two%3F%20Door%20one%3F%20Onstage%3F%20Backstage%3F%26quot%3B%20But%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20all%20the%20uncertainty%20and%20anxiety%2C%20there's%20one%20person%20who%20never%20appears%20in%20her%20dreams%3A%20Bob%20Barker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20couldn't%20get%20in%20here%20if%20he%20tried%2C%26quot%3B%20Hallstrom%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fdavid-kushner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EDavid%20Kushner%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20r