E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20buzz%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvinod-khosla-universal-basic-income-ai-job-loss-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20snatching%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20us%20poor%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20our%20robot%20overlords%20in%20waiting%20have%20been%20listening%2C%20they've%20heard%20many%20a%20tech%20leader%20and%20thinker%20repeat%20the%20idea%20that%20AI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-wont-take-your-job-someone-using-it-will-quote-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewon't%20take%20your%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20someone%20who%20knows%20how%20to%20use%20it%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20notion%20got%20thrust%20back%20into%20the%20spotlight%20recently%20when%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20said%20that%20students%20worried%20that%20AI%20will%20sideline%20them%20should%20double%20down%20on%20learning%20to%20use%20the%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20an%20approach%20that%20he%20said%20worked%20for%20him%20with%20computer%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20confident%20that%20there%20will%20be%20lots%20of%20jobs%20and%20also%20that%20many%20of%20them%20will%20look%20somewhat%20different%20than%20the%20jobs%20of%20today%2C%20but%20we%20never%20seem%20to%20run%20out%20of%20stuff%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-young-people-worried-about-ai-should-learn-tech-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAltman%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20taped%20interview%20with%20Indeed%20CEO%20Chris%20Hyams%20released%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman's%20sunny%20take%20was%20at%20odds%20with%20one%20offered%20days%20earlier%20by%20Silicon%20Valley%20investor%20Vinod%20Khosla%2C%20who%20warned%20that%20AI%20would%20one%20day%20be%20able%20to%20take%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvinod-khosla-universal-basic-income-ai-job-loss-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E80%25%20of%20the%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2080%25%20of%20jobs.%20He%20also%20said%20that%2C%20unlike%20with%20earlier%20tech%20waves%2C%20workers%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20simply%20build%20their%20skills%20to%20inoculate%20themselves%20against%20job%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20despite%20all%20the%20worrying%20about%20how%20AI%20might%20pillory%20the%20job%20market%2C%20people%20from%20execs%20to%20students%20appear%20to%20be%20pushing%20ahead%20with%20what%20Altman%20would%20recommend%3A%20going%20deep%20on%20the%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20noted%20that%20computer%20programming%20was%20already%20popular%20when%20he%20was%20in%20school%20but%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20like%26quot%3B%20today.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20say%20the%20same%20things%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0many%20of%20the%20same%20things%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0they%20say%20about%20AI%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242e47c15-c9d2-41b8-8165-9bcfd3109d99%5C%22%3EHumans%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20point%20for%20the%20don't-worry%20camp%20came%20from%20a%20new%20Indeed%20study%20identifying%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hiringlab.org%2F2024%2F09%2F25%2Fartificial-intelligence-skills-at-work%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2%2C800%20work%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20job%20site's%20researchers%2C%20using%20lengthy%20prompts%20with%20a%20generative%20AI%20tool%2C%20determined%20that%20none%20of%20those%20skills%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20likely%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20GenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESvenja%20Gudell%2C%20Indeed's%20chief%20economist%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20so-called%20upskilling%20can%20offer%20big%20benefits%20but%20isn't%20%26quot%3Bmagic.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20some%20people%20could%20still%20lose%20their%20jobs%20due%20to%20technological%20advancements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey'll%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20use%20these%20tools.%20It%20won't%20be%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20Gudell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bat%20least%20with%20the%20technology%20that%20we're%20seeing%20today%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20AI%20automation%20where%20you%20have%20smart%20robots%20working%20in%20warehouses%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhosla%2C%20who%20cofounded%20Sun%20Microsystems%20and%20who%20has%20invested%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20had%20warned%20that%20bipedal%20robots%20were%20one%20of%20the%20developments%20that%20would%20imperil%20humans'%20abilities%20to%20hang%20onto%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20robots%20show%20up%20to%20stock%20store%20shelves%2C%20they'd%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20come%20for%20desk%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Indeed's%20Gudell%20said%2C%20there's%20been%20a%20pickup%20in%20demand%20and%20pay%20for%20people%20well-versed%20in%20aspects%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20prompt%20engineer%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you're%20a%20machine%20learning%20engineer%20that%20can%20actually%20program%20some%20of%20this%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20getting%20a%20very%20healthy%20wage%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20Gudell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20professions%20that%20would%20appear%20most%20at%20risk%20of%20an%20AI%20takeover%20is%20coding.%20Yet%2C%20as%20BI%20previously%20reported%2C%20some%20experienced%20software%20engineers%20contend%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-threaten-jobs-of-coders-who-dont-shift-their-focus-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20will%20help%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20get%20more%20done%20without%20taking%20over%20their%20jobs%20because%20their%20work%20extends%20well%20beyond%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22653e0433-efd1-4f58-872b-0e198cde70cf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKids%20are%20still%20learning%20to%20code%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20worries%20about%20an%20AI%20job-pocalypse%20aren't%20deterring%20some%20people%20from%20going%20big%20on%20tech%2C%20as%20Altman%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdward%20Kim%20is%20vice%20president%20of%20education%20and%20training%20at%20Code%20Ninjas.%20The%20company%20teaches%20software%20engineering%20to%20kids%20ages%20five%20to%2014%20through%20in-person%20classes%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20the%20company%20is%20seeing%20strong%20demand%20from%20people%20hoping%20to%20open%20franchise%20locations.%20Within%20two%20years%2C%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20add%20200%20locations%20on%20top%20of%20the%20more%20than%20350%20it%20has%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20professional%20coders%20Kim%20talks%20to%20already%20use%20AI%20to%20do%20things%20like%20generating%20starter%20code.%20But%20these%20engineers%20aren't%20that%20worried%20about%20getting%20pushed%20out%20of%20their%20jobs%2C%20he%20said%2C%20because%20coders%20are%20working%20for%20people%20who%20need%20them%20to%20do%20more%20than%20just%20write%20line%20after%20line%20in%20various%20programming%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployers%20need%20%26quot%3Bsomeone%20with%20a%20real-world%20context%20to%20put%20the%20right%20adaptation%20to%20it%2C%20to%20make%20it%20applicable%20to%20something%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20so%20it%20can%20be%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20said%20(aka%3A%20be%20a%20human).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20Code%20Ninjas'%20students%20might%20take%20around%2018%20months%20to%20become%20proficient%20in%20a%20new%20language.%20Now%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it's%20closer%20to%20six%20to%2012%20months%20for%20those%20same%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20that%20the%20kids%20that%20are%20coming%20up%20have%20an%20increasing%20thirst%20for%20this%20type%20of%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20desire%20to%20learn%20that%20Altman%20indicated%20he%20showed%20back%20when%20he%20was%20a%20student.%20He%20said%20computer%20programming%20had%20been%20a%20net%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20made%20some%20classes%20of%20jobs%20go%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said.%20Still%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20made%20way%20more%20new%20things%20happen%20and%20also%20given%20us%20the%20ability%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20something%20to%20share%20about%20what%20you're%20seeing%20in%20the%20workplace%20or%20in%20your%20job%20search%3F%20Business%20Insider%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Email%20our%20workplace%20team%20from%20a%20nonwork%20device%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Athegrind%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethegrind%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20with%20your%20story%2C%20or%20ask%20for%20one%20of%20our%20reporter's%20Signal%20numbers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-wont-take-as-many-jobs-as-feared-altman-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727602022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f7134075c877a99b617a09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-wont-take-as-many-jobs-as-feared-altman-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sam%20Altman%20says%20students%20should%20learn%20AI%20to%20keep%20jobs.%20Meantime%2C%20a%20study%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20human%20skills%20weren't%20%26quot%3Bvery%20likely%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20GenAI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-wont-take-as-many-jobs-as-feared-altman-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Position%2C%20But%20Responsibility%26quot%3B%3A%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20On%20Getting%20Top%20Post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20not%20a%20position%2C%20but%20a%20responsibility%2C%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%20today%2C%20hours%20after%20his%20father%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20announced%20his%20elevation%20to%20the%20top%20post.%20The%2046-year-old%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20state%20minister%20in%20charge%20of%20youth%20welfare%20and%20sports%20development%2C%20has%20also%20been%20handed%20over%20the%20planning%20and%20development%20portfolio%20in%20the%20latest%20cabinet%20reshuffle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRealizing%20that%20'Deputy%20Chief%20Minister'%20is%20not%20a%20position%20but%20a%20responsibility...%20we%20will%20work%20together%20with%20our%20fellow%20Ministers%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Chief%20Minister%20on%20the%20path%20paved%20by%20Father%20Periyar%20-%20Perarinjar%20Anna%20-%20Muthamizharinjar%20Kalainar%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BFather%20Periyar%26quot%3B%20refers%20to%20social%20activist%20and%20Tamil%20icon%20Periyar%2C%20while%20%26quot%3BKalainar%26quot%3B%20refers%20to%20veteran%20DMK%20leader%20and%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20grandfather%2C%20late%20M%20Karunanidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20announcement%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20today%20visited%20the%20memorial%20of%20M%20Karunanidhi%20in%20Chennai.%20He%20also%20visited%20Periyar's%20memorial%20and%20the%20homes%20of%20his%20grandfather%20at%20Gopalapuram%20and%20CIT%20Colony%20in%20Chennai.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20photographs%2C%20his%20aunt%20and%20senior%20DMK%20leader%20K%20Kanimozhi%20is%20seen%20congratulating%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20slammed%20the%20DMK%20over%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20elevation%20to%20the%20top%20post%20and%20said%20the%20party's%20history%20has%20been%20marked%20with%20%26quot%3Byears%20of%20betrayal%20of%20the%20people%20and%20prioritising%20family%20interests%20over%20public%20welfare%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20being%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20DMK%20has%20denied%20its%20partners%20a%20share%20in%20power%20and%20instead%20appointed%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumnus%20of%20Loyola%20College%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20has%20worked%20in%20several%20movies%20as%20an%20actor%20and%20producer%20before%20an%20all-out%20foray%20into%20politics.%20He%20has%20led%20the%20DMK's%20student%20wing%20and%20was%20among%20the%20key%20faces%20of%20the%20party's%202021%20campaign%20for%20the%202021%20state%20polls%20in%20which%20it%20scored%20a%20thumping%20win.%20He%20was%20inducted%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20leader%20made%20national%20headlines%20last%20year%20when%20his%20remarks%20likening%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20to%20dengue%20and%20malaria%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%20Stressing%20that%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20he%20said%20at%20an%20event%2C%20%26quot%3BSanatana%20is%20like%20malaria%20and%20dengue%20and%20so%20it%20must%20be%20eradicated%20and%20not%20opposed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20claimed%20that%20the%20remark%20was%20a%20genocidal%20call%20and%20targeted%20Congress%20which%20was%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20had%20said%20he%20never%20called%20for%20genocide.%20%26quot%3BSanatana%20Dharma%20is%20a%20principle%20that%20divides%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%20Uprooting%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20upholding%20humanity%20and%20human%20equality.%20I%20stand%20firmly%20by%20every%20word%20I%20have%20spoken.%20I%20spoke%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20oppressed%20and%20marginalized%2C%20who%20suffer%20due%20to%20the%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727602020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ffp1napl_udhayanidhi-stalin_625x300_29_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fudhayanidhi-stalin-tamil-nadu-not-position-but-responsibility-udhayanidhi-stalin-on-getting-top-post-6676283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20not%20a%20position%2C%20but%20a%20responsibility%2C%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%20today%2C%20hours%20after%20his%20father%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20announced%20his%20elevation%20to%20the%20top%20post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fudhayanidhi-stalin-tamil-nadu-not-position-but-responsibility-udhayanidhi-stalin-on-getting-top-post-6676283%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22L%26amp%3BT%20Semicon%20expects%20chip%20production%20to%20start%20in%202%20yrs%3B%20to%20set%20up%20unit%20later%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727601768000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-09%2F08%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1725817921-438.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fl-t-semicon-expects-its-chip-production-to-start-in-2-yrs-to-set-up-unit-later-124092900243_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Electronics%2C%20Micron%2C%20CG%20Power%20and%20Kaynes%20Technologies%20are%20setting%20up%20semiconductor%20units%20in%20India%20with%20a%20cumulative%20investment%20of%20Rs%201.52%20lakh%20crore%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fl-t-semicon-expects-its-chip-production-to-start-in-2-yrs-to-set-up-unit-later-124092900243_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%