.com%2Fharris-trump-presidential-election-50-days-vance-walz-electoral-math-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20presidential%20election%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20when%20the%20stock%20market%20rises%2C%20and%20unemployment%20and%20inflation%20remain%20low%2C%20the%20incumbent%20party%20remains%20in%20power.%20The%20opposite%20is%20true%20when%20stocks%20fall%20and%20unemployment%20and%20inflation%20climb%2C%20according%20to%20LPL%20Financial's%20Chief%20Technical%20Strategist%20Adam%20Turnquist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20performance%20from%20August%20to%20October%20before%20the%20election%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Misery%20Index%2C%20which%20tracks%20the%20sum%20of%20inflation%20and%20unemployment%2C%20have%20historically%20been%20accurate%20predictors%20of%20the%20election%20outcome%20%E2%80%94%20and%20both%20are%20spelling%20out%20a%20Harris%20presidency%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20intuitive%20sense%3A%20if%20the%20economy%20is%20doing%20well%2C%20voters%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20content%20with%20the%20existing%20administration%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%20But%20before%20you%20bet%20on%20the%20election%20outcome%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20other%20factors%20you%20should%20consider%2C%20according%20to%20market%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254fd337e-85a8-42ed-85bf-3521b3a1a452%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarkets%20are%20pointing%20to%20Harris%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%201984%2C%20the%20incumbent%20party%20has%20been%20reelected%20if%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20was%20positive%20or%20voted%20out%20if%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20was%20negative%20in%20the%20three-month%20period%20from%20August%20to%20October%20before%20the%20election%2C%20according%20to%20Comerica%20Wealth%20Management.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20gained%2010%25%20since%20August%205%2C%20and%20if%20it%20keeps%20going%20up%2C%20a%20Harris%20victory%20seems%20imminent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20the%20so-called%20Misery%20Index%20is%20flashing%20a%20Harris%20victory.%20The%20index%20measures%20economic%20health%20calculated%20by%20adding%20the%20seasonally-adjusted%20unemployment%20rate%20and%20the%20annual%20inflation%20rate.%20Since%201980%2C%20the%20incumbent%20party%20has%20lost%20every%20contest%20when%20the%20three-month%20average%20of%20the%20Misery%20Index%20increases%20year-over-year%20leading%20up%20to%20election%20day%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Misery%20Index%20has%20accurately%20predicted%20every%20election%20since%201980.%20It%20stands%20at%207.118%20compared%20to%207.335%20last%20October%2C%20signaling%20a%20Harris%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d0650bfa-def6-4b4a-8941-e43c49e4e102%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvestors%20beware%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20should%20note%20that%20these%20indicators%20don't%20guarantee%20the%20election%20outcome%2C%20especially%20in%20today's%20heightened-risk%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20the%20incumbent%20party%20this%20year%20switched%20candidates%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rare%20occurrence%20highlighting%20that%20historical%20precedent%20isn't%20always%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20factors%20at%20play%20too%2C%20according%20to%20Turnquist.%20Volatility%20usually%20increases%20in%20election%20years%2C%20but%20this%20year%20promises%20be%20extra%20volatile%20due%20to%20geopolitical%20uncertainty%2C%20a%20cooling%20economy%2C%20and%20disruptive%20policies.%20While%20policies%20discussed%20during%20the%20campaign%20trail%20won't%20necessarily%20be%20implemented%20in%20practice%2C%20Turnquist%20sees%20some%20of%20the%20proposals%20being%20discussed%20as%20having%20more%20disruptive%20potential%20than%20previous%20cycles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20November%20is%20rapidly%20approaching%2C%20Turnquist%20said%20it's%20still%20too%20early%20to%20bet%20on%20the%20Misery%20Index%20readings.%20The%20last%20two%20non-farm%20payroll%20numbers%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20economists'%20estimates%2C%20which%20Turnquist%20sees%20as%20cause%20for%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Federal%20Reserve%20Chairman%20Jerome%20Powell%20recently%20stated%20that%20the%20labor%20market%20was%20on%20solid%20footing%2C%20Turnquist%20isn't%20so%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20labor%20market%20still%20seems%20to%20be%20on%20trial%2C%26quot%3B%20Turnquist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20September%20data%20continues%20to%20fall%20below%20expectations%2C%20Turnquist%20believes%20the%20market%20will%20price%20in%20more%20rate%20cuts%2C%20and%20stocks%20could%20slide.%20A%20pullback%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20experienced%20during%20the%20first%20week%20of%20August%20this%20year%20isn't%20out%20of%20the%20question%2C%20in%20his%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20a%20correction%20would%20not%20be%20terribly%20surprising%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Turnquist%20said.%20If%20the%20stock%20market%20declines%2C%20the%20outlook%20for%20a%20Harris%20victory%20could%20quickly%20sour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELynch%20agrees%20with%20Turnquist.%20Harris%20has%2015%20basis%20points%20of%20leeway%20before%20the%20Misery%20Index%20exceeds%20October%202023's%20reading%2C%20and%20September's%20unemployment%20report%20could%20very%20well%20push%20the%20index%20over%20the%20edge%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20choppy%20path%20for%20the%20stock%20market%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20election.%20While%20these%20indicators%20might%20be%20flashing%20a%20Harris%20victory%20for%20now%2C%20nothing's%20set%20in%20stone%20leading%20up%20to%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-prediction-stock-market-indicators-trump-harris-win-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727601122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f598bb75c877a99