-warns-against-taking-ozempic-get-beach-body-ready-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%20against%20using%20weight-loss%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bquick%20fix.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%20England%20medical%20director%2C%20Stephen%20Powis%2C%20said%20in%20June%20that%20while%20such%20drugs%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20a%20powerful%20part%20of%20our%20arsenal%20dealing%20with%20obesity%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20should%20%26quot%3Bnot%20be%20abused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDrugs%20including%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20should%20only%20be%20used%20by%20people%20prescribed%20them%20for%20obesity%20or%20diabetes.%20I'm%20worried%20about%20reports%20that%20people%20are%20misusing%20them%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20not%20intended%20as%20a%20quick%20fix%20for%20people%20trying%20to%20get%20'beach%20body%20ready%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-corden-says-did-not-lose-weight-ozempic-emotional-eating-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727599686000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6d09775c877a99b613e15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-corden-says-did-not-lose-weight-ozempic-emotional-eating-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weight-loss%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20have%20become%20household%20names%20in%20recent%20years.%20But%20here's%20why%20they%20may%20not%20work%20for%20everyone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ecrosbie%40businessinsider.com%20(Eve%20Crosbie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-corden-says-did-not-lose-weight-ozempic-emotional-eating-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPeople%20Will%20Troll%20Me%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Grammy%20Winner%20Ricky%20Kej%20Blasts%20Air%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-American%20composer%20Ricky%20Kej%20has%20yet%20again%20publicly%20blasted%20Air%20India%20after%20he%20had%20to%20allegedly%20wait%20for%20nearly%20an%20hour%20over%20the%20payment%20of%20his%20excess%20baggage%20at%20the%20airport.%20Taking%20to%20his%20official%20X%20account%20today%2C%20Mr%20Kej%2C%20a%20three-time%20Grammy%20winner%2C%20detailed%20two%20incidents%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FALSO%2520READ%2520%7C%C2%A0Air%2520India%2520Passenger%2520Finds%2520Cockroach%2520In%2520Food%2520On%2520Delhi-New%2520York%2520Flight%2C%2520Airline%2520Responds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAir%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20apparently%20was%20the%20fifth%20time%20in%20a%20year%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fricky-kej-grammy-winner-flight-horror-air-india-not-befitting-reputed-brand-grammy-winning-composer-blasts-air-india-6253792%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efaced%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20airline%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20certain%20a%20few%20people%20will%20troll%20me%2C%20asking%20me%20why%20I%20keep%20doing%20this%20to%20myself..%20travel%20through%20such%20a%20terrible%20airline%2C%20but%20I%20will%20continuously%20give%20them%20chances%20and%20criticize%20them%20for%20errors%2C%20till%20they%20improve%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20responded%20to%20his%20post%2C%20saying%20it%20%26quot%3Bsincerely%20regrets%20the%20inconvenience%20experienced%26quot%3B%20during%20his%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20Incident%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarrating%20the%20first%20incident%2C%20which%20he%20said%20took%20place%20when%20he%20was%20flying%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Bengaluru%20on%20September%2014%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Far-rahmans-selfie-with-zakir-hussain-shankar-mahadevan-its-raining-grammys-for-india-4997494%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERicky%20Kej%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20reached%20the%20Air%20India%20check-in%20line%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Airport.%20Was%20flying%20business%20class.%20As%20always%20the%20lady%20at%20the%20counter%20was%20distracted%2C%20had%20to%20get%20her%20attention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20not%20slept%20for%202%20days%20and%20was%20travelling%20directly%20after%20performing%20a%20concert%20at%20the%20ITC%20Maurya.%20My%20bag%20was%20overweight%20by%206%20kgs%2C%20I%20immediately%20offered%20to%20pay%2C%20as%20I%20always%20do.%20They%20told%20me%20I%20needed%20to%20go%20to%20a%20counter%20which%20was%20quite%20a%20walk%20away%20just%20to%20pay.%20I%20requested%20them%20to%20bring%20the%20wireless%20payment%20machine%20to%20the%20check-in%20counter%20like%20all%20the%20other%20airlines%20do%20(I%20routinely%20pay%20for%20excess%20baggage%20due%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20my%20profession)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2043-year-old%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E(Read%20the%20entire%20thread)%20So%2C%20I%20thought%20a%20lot%20about%20this%2C%20waited%20to%20cool%20off%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20post%20calmly.%20Two%20incidents%20that%20happened%20recently%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fairindia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AirIndia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20am%20certain%20a%20few%20people%20will%20troll%20me%2C%20asking%20me%20why%20do%20I%20keep%20doing%20this%20to%20myself..%20travel%20through%20such%20a%20terrible%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjuvxPJm1pQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FjuvxPJm1pQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ricky%20Kej%20(%40rickykej)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frickykej%2Fstatus%2F1840258832179630368%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20refused%20(Devika%2C%20Ravi%20Kumar%2C%20Mukeeta%20and%20Neha).%20So%20I%20walked%20to%20the%20counter%20they%20directed%20me%20to.%20The%20person%20at%20that%20counter%20(Sunil)%20refused%20to%20even%20look%20in%20my%20direction%20and%20rudely%20said%20he%20was%20busy%20-%20either%20I%20could%20wait%20there%20for%20a%20while%20or%20he%20directed%20me%20to%20their%20ticketing%20counter%20which%20is%20at%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20terminal.%20I%20refused%20both%20options%20and%20went%20back%20to%20the%20check-in%20counter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kej%20said%20they%20told%20him%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20they%20could%20do%26quot%3B%20and%20made%20a%20call%20to%20Sunil%20and%20told%20him%20to%20accept%20his%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20the%20walk%20back%20to%20Sunil%20(for%20a%20second%20time).%20I%20offered%20to%20pay%20by%20UPI.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20any%20credit%20cards%20or%20cash.%20He%20flatly%20refused%20UPI%20(Shocking%20for%20an%20Indian%20brand).%20He%20said%20UPI%20is%20useless%20and%20Air%20India%20does%20not%20accept%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20protested..%20told%20him%20that%20I%20have%20UPI%20attached%20with%20multiple%20banks%20and%20can%20ensure%20the%20payment%20goes%20through%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20talk%20to%20me%20further.%20I%20went%20back%20to%20the%20check-in%20counter.%20They%20told%20me%20there%20was%20nothing%20they%20could%20do%20and%20offered%20to%20cancel%20my%20ticket%20instead!!%20They%20refused%20to%20give%20me%20any%20details%20on%20a%20refund%20and%20gave%20me%20back%20my%20suitcase.%20Then%20I%20argued%20with%20them%20-%20told%20them%20I%20am%20sleep%20deprived%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20on%20the%20flight...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinally%20after%2050%20minutes%20of%20this%20ordeal%2C%20and%20almost%20missing%20my%20flight%2C%20on%20my%20insistence%2C%20Devika%20called%20Sunil..%20he%20finally%20agreed%20to%20come%20to%20the%20check-in%20counter%20(where%20I%20was)%20with%20the%20wireless%20machine%20and%20accepted%20the%20UPI%20payment%20which%20went%20through%20effortlessly%20in%20a%20few%20seconds.%20I%20left%20for%20security%20check%20and%20boarded%20the%20flight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20classical%20musician%20said%20he%20personally%20feels%20this%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsystemic%20issue%26quot%3B%20with%20Air%20India%20where%20they%20%26quot%3Bjust%20do%20not%20care%26quot%3B%20about%20their%20loyal%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20named%20all%20the%20offensive%20staff%2C%20and%20would%20really%20like%20to%20know%20how%20Air%20India%20deals%20with%20this%20issue%20I%20had.%20I%20should%20have%20never%20gone%20through%20that%2050-minute%20ordeal%20when%20they%20could%20have%20settled%20the%20payment%20within%20seconds.%20This%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20the%20airline%20bullying%20a%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%20Incident%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20second%20incident%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcockroaches-dirty-toilet-grammy-award-winner-ricky-kej-shares-harrowing-experience-at-mumbai-hotel-5254425%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERicky%20Kej%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20was%20flying%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20San%20Francisco%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-to-give-400-million-makeover-to-over-half-of-its-fleet-6588629%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAir%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0flight%20on%20September%2020%20when%20one%20of%20the%20attendants%20continuously%20turned%20off%20a%20blue%20light%20(call%20for%20service)%20turned%20on%20by%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20flying%20economy%2C%20a%20direct%20flight%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20San%20Francisco.%20Almost%20a%2017-hour%20flight.%20I%20