a-economy-oil-war-revenue-crude-prices-opec-production-cut-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russian%20economy%20right%20now%20is%20being%20propped%20up%20by%20large%20amounts%20of%20government%20spending%2C%20so%20there's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20slowdown%20in%20any%20sector%20in%20the%20economy%20that%20the%20Russia%20government%20is%20buying%20supplies%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20Zagorsky%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20Kremlin%20purchasing%20uniforms%2C%20boots%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20food%20as%20part%20of%20its%20war%20efforts%20against%20Ukraine.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20there%20was%20no%20war%2C%20oh%20yes%2C%20I%20think%20there'd%20be%20an%20immediate%20recession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20war%20continues%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20a%20downturn%20is%20uncertain%2C%20according%20to%20Yuriy%20Gorodnichenko%2C%20an%20economist%20and%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California-Berkeley%20who%20also%20sees%20trouble%20ahead%20for%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nation%20is%20reportedly%20setting%20aside%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-09-23%2Frussia-budget-plans-show-no-let-up-in-putin-s-war-on-ukraine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord%2013.2%20trillion%20rubles%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20defense%20budget%20next%20year%2C%20which%20should%20help%20stimulate%20its%20economy.%20However%2C%20that%20kind%20of%20monster%20spending%20can't%20continue%20forever%2C%20Gorodnichenko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20government%20money%2C%20they%20can%20keep%20the%20economy%20afloat%2C%20but%20at%20some%20point%20the%20government%20is%20going%20to%20run%20out%20of%20money%2C%20so%20they'll%20have%20to%20stop%2C%20and%20they'll%20have%20a%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286bdb8ac-c7fb-44c6-ad24-a3ae0cf8d4fe%5C%22%3EMoscow's%20economic%20issues%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20red%20flags%20waving%20inside%20Russia's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20problems%2C%20Zagorsky%20said.%20According%20to%20Russia's%20official%20statistics%20service%2C%20consumer%20prices%20climbed%209%25%20year-over-year%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Zagorsky%20speculated%20that%20inflation%20could%20be%20running%20way%20hotter%20than%20that.%20The%20Bank%20of%20Russia%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbr.ru%2Feng%2Fpress%2Fkeypr%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOn%252013%2520September%25202024%252C%2520the%2CCurrent%2520inflationary%2520pressures%2520remain%2520high.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiked%20rates%20to%2019%25%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20September%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20they%20have%20been%20since%20the%20Ukraine%20invasion%C2%A0began%20%E2%80%94%20which%20prompted%20central%20bankers%20to%20take%20emergency%20policy%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20suggests%20to%20me%20that%20inflation%20might%20actually%20be%20really%20higher%2C%20and%20they're%20a%20little%20bit%20underreporting%2C%26quot%3B%20Zagorsky%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20Soviet%20Union's%20practice%20of%20understating%20its%20inflation%20numbers%20during%20the%20Cold%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20economy%20is%20also%20being%20plagued%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Frussia-financial-flows-sanctions-us-dollar-access-treasury-ukraine-war-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurrency%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gorodnichenko%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20Russia's%20limited%20access%20to%20the%20dollar%20as%20the%20result%20of%20Western%20sanctions.%20That's%20crimped%20Moscow%20ability%20to%20trade%2C%20especially%20for%20its%20oil%20and%20crude%20products%2C%20which%20make%20up%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20its%20total%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20turned%20to%20alternative%20currencies%2C%20like%20China's%20yuan%2C%20to%20bolster%20its%20balance%20sheet%20and%20keep%20trade%20humming%20along.%20But%20now%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Frussia-economy-china-yuan-sanctions-bank-payments-trade-transfers-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereminibi%20is%20in%20short%20supply%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Chinese%20firms%20increasingly%20hesitant%20to%20do%20business%20with%20Russia%20in%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted%20by%20secondary%20sanctions%20from%20the%20US%20and%20other%20Western%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia%20is%20making%20fewer%20sales%20to%20China%2C%20or%20receiving%20less%20for%20whatever%20volumes%2C%20physical%20volumes%20they%20send%20to%20China.%20All%20...%20are%20contributing%20factors%20to%20economic%20problems%20in%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20Gorodnichenko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20Gorodnichenko%20predicted%20Russia%20could%20see%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-collapse-recession-moscow-ukraine-war-us-dollar-energy-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esevere%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20next%20year%20if%20the%20nation%20ran%20out%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20that%20will%20happen%20in%20the%20next%20year%2C%20he%20said%2C%20though%20he%20noted%20that%20the%20nation's%20oil%20revenue%20has%20dropped%20as%20military%20spending%20has%20climbed.%20That's%20partially%20been%20a%20result%20of%20crude-oil%20prices%20falling%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia%20is%20not%20only%20facing%20a%20reduction%20in%20demand%20for%20its%20product%2C%20but%20a%20rather%20dramatic%20fall%20in%20the%20price.%20This%20is%20kind%20of%20a%20double-whammy%2C%26quot%3B%20Zagorsky%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20pretty%20simple%20story.%20The%20question%20is%20how%20long%20can%20the%20Russian%20economy%20keep%20going%20in%20the%20face%20of%20these%20big%20headwinds%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Zagorsky%20nor