%20yesterday%20(11%20am%20Lebanon%20time)%2C%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BHassan%20Nasrallah%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20terrorize%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Hezbollah%20confirmed%20the%20news.%20%26quot%3BSayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah...%20has%20joined%20his%20great%2C%20immortal%20martyr%20comrades%20whom%20he%20led%20for%20about%2030%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Israel%20Boosted%20Spies%20In%20Fight%20Against%20Hezbollah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20Israel's%20recent%20successes%20against%20Hezbollah%20are%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20the%20country's%20decision%20to%20devote%20far%20more%20intelligence%20resources%20to%20target%20Hezbollah%20after%20the%202006%20war%20with%20the%20Iran-backed%20group.%20The%20Israeli%20army%20and%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20failed%20to%20score%20a%20decisive%20victory%20in%20that%2034-day%20conflict.%20The%20war%20ended%20with%20a%20UN-brokered%20cease-fire%20and%20allowed%20Hezbollah%2C%20despite%20losses%2C%20to%20regroup%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20next%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20Israel%20deployed%20a%20lot%20of%20resources%20to%20collect%20information%20about%20Hezbollah's%20leadership%20and%20strategy.%20Unit%208200%2C%20Israel's%20signals%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20built%20cutting-edge%20cyber%20tools%20to%20better%20intercept%20Hezbollah's%20cellphones%20and%20other%20communications%2C%20the%20NYT%20report%20said.%20New%20teams%20were%20created%20within%20combat%20ranks%20to%20ensure%20that%20valuable%20information%20was%20quickly%20passed%20on%20to%20soldiers%20and%20the%20air%20force%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Pager%20Bombs%20And%20Nasrallah's%20Admission%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20televised%20speech%2C%20Nasrallah%20had%20said%20Hezbollah%20suffered%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20blow%26quot%3B%20after%20Israel%20detonated%20explosive-laden%20pagers%20and%20hand-held%20radios.%20The%20attacks%20killed%2037%20people%20and%20wounded%20nearly%203%2C000%20people%20in%20two%20days.%20Nasrallah%20had%20then%20warned%20Israel%20of%20%26quot%3Btough%20retribution%20and%20just%20punishment%2C%20where%20it%20expects%20it%20and%20where%20it%20does%20not%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Lebanese%20investigation%20found%20that%20the%20pagers%20had%20been%20booby-trapped%2C%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20members%20had%20started%20communicating%20via%20pagers%20and%20walkie-talkies%20after%20Israel%20penetrated%20cellphones.%20But%20that%20did%20not%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mossad%2C%20the%20NYT%20report%20said%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20created%20a%20shell%20company%20in%20Budapest%20and%20made%20the%20pagers%20under%20license%20from%20a%20company%20in%20Taiwan.%20Before%20the%20pagers%20arrived%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Israeli%20operatives%20installed%20explosives%20inside%20them.%20The%20operation%20was%20scaled%20to%20produce%20thousands%20of%20pagers%2C%20requiring%20sophisticated%20manufacturing%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETop%20Hezbollah%20Leaders%20Targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NYT%20report%2C%20Israel's%20investment%20in%20greater%20intelligence%20gathering%20first%20paid%20off%20in%202008%20when%20Mossad%20worked%20with%20the%20CIA%20to%20kill%20top%20Hezbollah%20operative%2C%20Imad%20Mugniyah%2C%20in%20Syria.%20In%202020%2C%20Qassim%20Suleimani%2C%20who%20headed%20Iran's%20Quds%20Force%2C%20flew%20to%20Syria's%20Damascus%20and%20drove%20in%20a%20convoy%20to%20Beirut%20to%20meet%20Nasrallah.%20Israel%20did%20not%20try%20to%20kill%20Nasrallah%20then%20for%20fear%20of%20starting%20a%20war.%20It%20passed%20on%20the%20information%20to%20the%20US%20and%20Suleimani%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20drone%20strike%20at%20Baghdad%20airport%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20October%207%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israeli%20cities%20set%20off%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20As%20Israel's%20counterstrike%20set%20off%20a%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Hezbollah%20started%20targeting%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20Tel%20Aviv%20went%20all-out%20against%20Hezbollah.%20A%20strike%20on%20July%2030%20killed%20Fuad%20Shukr%2C%20one%20of%20the%20group's%20top%20military%20commanders.%20About%20three%20weeks%20later%2C%20a%20strike%20killed%20Ibrahim%20Aqil%2C%20head%20of%20Hezbollah's%20elite%20Radwan%20Force%2C%20and%2015%20other%20commanders.%20Days%20later%2C%20another%20strike%20killed%20Ibrahim%20Mohammed%20Kobeissi%2C%20who%20commanded%20several%20Hezbollah%20units%2C%20including%20a%20guided%20missiles%20unit.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Mohammed%20Srur%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Hezbollah's%20drone%20unit%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChip%20Usher%2C%20a%20former%20CIA%20analyst%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20Israeli%20intelligence%2C%20has%20told%20NYT%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20secrets%20of%20their%20success%20come%20down%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20factors.%20They%20have%20a%20fairly%20defined%20target%20deck.%20That%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20them%20to%20bring%20a%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20focus%20to%20what%20they%20do.%20They're%20in%20a%20shadow%20war%20with%20Hezbollah%20and%20Iran.%20And%20they're%20extraordinarily%20patient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727597640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fm6n38q2o_nasrallah_625x300_29_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhassan-nasrallah-hezbollah-iran-spy-told-israel-hezbollah-chiefs-location-before-airstrike-report-6675770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20before%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Sayyed%2