2Farticleshow%2F113783290.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMost%20Difficult%20Decision%26quot%3B%3A%20Thai%20Farmer%20Forced%20To%20Kill%20Over%20100%20Crocodiles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20farmer%20in%20northern%20Thailand%20was%20forced%20to%20cull%20more%20than%20100%20crocodiles%20from%20his%20farm%20as%20heavy%20floods%20raised%20fears%20that%20they%20could%20escape%20and%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20human%20lives.%20Natthapak%20Khumkad%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20crocodile%20farm%20in%20Lamphun%2C%20explained%20that%20days%20of%20relentless%20rain%20had%20severely%20damaged%20the%20enclosures%20holding%20his%20Siamese%20crocodiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20animals%20at%20risk%20of%20escaping%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20kill%20125%20crocodiles%2C%20which%20measured%20up%20to%20three%20meters%20long.%20Mr%20Khumkad%20was%20particularly%20concerned%20that%20the%20reptiles%20might%20roam%20the%20flooded%20countryside%2C%20potentially%20attacking%20locals%20and%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20reported%20by%20CNN%20on%20Friday%2C%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Lamphun%20province%20following%20devastating%20monsoon%20rains%20that%20have%20swept%20across%20the%20region.%20In%20September%2C%20northern%20Thailand%20was%20hit%20by%20intense%20monsoon%20rains%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20landslides%20and%20floods%20that%20killed%20over%2020%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20make%20the%20most%20difficult%20decision%20of%20my%20life%20to%20kill%20them%20all.%20My%20family%20and%20I%20discussed%20if%20the%20wall%20collapsed%20the%20damage%20to%20people's%20lives%20would%20be%20far%20bigger%20than%20we%20can%20control.%20It%20would%20involve%20people's%20lives%20and%20public%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20farmer%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Natthapak%20Khumkad%20showed%20the%20eroded%20walls%20of%20the%20crocodile%20pond%20and%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20primary%20reason%20that%20forced%20me%20to%20make%20an%20urgent%20decision.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20it%20rained%20heavily%20non-stop.%20The%20underwater%20wall%20collapsed%2C%20which%20was%20very%20close%20to%20reaching%20the%20outer%20wall.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clarified%20that%20although%20his%20staff%20attempted%20to%20block%20off%20the%20area%20to%20fix%20the%20pond%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20the%20unceasing%20rain%20made%20the%20situation%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20crisis%20that%20required%20an%20extremely%20urgent%20decision.%20I%20had%20to%20use%20the%20last%20resort%2C%20which%20was%20to%20remove%20the%20crocodiles%20from%20the%20farm%20by%20slaughtering%20them.%20If%20it%20wasn't%20absolutely%20necessary%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20used%20this%20method.%20It%20was%20the%20best%2C%20fastest%2C%20and%20safest%20method%20in%20that%20situation%2C%20with%20the%20rain%20still%20pouring%20incessantly.%20Thank%20you%20for%20all%20the%20encouragement%20and%20understanding.%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Natthapak%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727597040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fclus14e_crocodile-farm_625x300_29_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmost-difficult-decision-thai-farmer-forced-to-kill-over-100-crocodiles-6675219%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20farmer%20in%20northern%20Thailand%20was%20forced%20to%20cull%20more%20than%20100%20crocodiles%20from%20his%20farm%20as%20heavy%20floods%20raised%20fears%20that%20they%20could%20escape%20and%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20human%20lives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rani%20Mukerji%20on%20her%20script%20choice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727596764000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2