itional%2013%25%20stake%20in%20Tata%20Autocomp%20Systems%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727595104000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-09%2F03%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1725362846-4971.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-sons-planning-to-buy-an-additional-13-stake-in-tata-autocomp-systems-124092900217_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Currently%2C%20Tata%20Sons%20holds%20a%2040%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Tata%20Autocomp%20Systems%2C%20while%20Tata%20Motors%20owns%2026%20per%20cent%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-sons-planning-to-buy-an-additional-13-stake-in-tata-autocomp-systems-124092900217_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-sons-planning-to-buy-an-additional-13-stake-in-tata-autocomp-systems-124092900217_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-sons-planning-to-buy-an-additional-13-stake-in-tata-autocomp-systems-124092900217_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20US%20Woman%20Trafficked%20Asians%20For%20Sex%20Racket%20For%20Politicians%2C%20Army%20Officers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20US%20woman%20has%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20running%20a%20high-end%20sex%20racket%20in%20the%20greater%20Boston%20area%20and%20the%20suburbs%20of%20Washington%20that%20served%20politicians%2C%20military%20officers%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20corporate%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHan%20Lee%2C%2042%2C%20appeared%20in%20Boston%20federal%20court%20on%20Friday%20to%20plead%20guilty%20to%20charges%20that%20she%20conspired%20to%20%26quot%3Bpersuade%2C%20induce%20and%20entice%26quot%3B%20primarily%20Asian%20women%20to%20travel%20to%20Massachusetts%20and%20Virginia%20to%20engage%20in%20prostitution%20and%20committed%20money%20laundering%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Massachusetts%20resident%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20in%20November%20last%20year%20along%20with%20Junmyung%20Lee%2C%2031%2C%20and%20James%20Lee%2C%2069.%20They%20were%20subsequently%20indicted%20by%20a%20federal%20grand%20jury%20in%20February%20for%20operating%20the%20prostitution%20racket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHan%20Lee%20faces%20up%20to%2025%20years%20in%20prison%20when%20she%20is%20sentenced%20in%20December.%20She%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20while%20she%20ran%20an%20illegal%20prostitution%20business%2C%20she%20did%20not%20force%20any%20women%20to%20engage%20in%20sex%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20They%20Operated%20The%20Sex%20Racket%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20prosecutors%2C%20from%20at%20least%20July%202020%2C%20Han%20Lee%20operated%20an%20interstate%20prostitution%20network%20with%20multiple%20brothels%20in%20Cambridge%20and%20Watertown%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20and%20Fairfax%20and%20Tysons%2C%20Virginia%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20established%20the%20infrastructure%20for%20these%20brothels%20in%20multiple%20states%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20%26quot%3Bpersuading%2C%20inducing%20and%20enticing%20women%20-%20primarily%20Asian%20women%20-%20to%20travel%20to%20Massachusetts%20and%20Virginia%20to%20engage%20in%20prostitution%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20further%20alleged%20that%20Han%20Lee%20and%20her%20aides%20coordinated%20the%20women's%20airline%20travel%20and%20transportation%20and%20permitted%20them%20to%20stay%20overnight%20in%20the%20brothel%20locations%20so%20they%20did%20not%20have%20to%20find%20lodging%20elsewhere%2C%20therefore%20enticing%20women%20to%20participate%20in%20their%20prostitution%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20protect%20and%20maintain%20the%20secrecy%20of%20the%20business%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20women%20did%20not%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20prostitution%20work%20inside%20apartment%20buildings%2C%20Han%20Lee%20and%2C%20allegedly%2C%20her%20co-defendants%20established%20house%20rules%20for%20the%20women%20during%20their%20stays%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharged%20%24350%20To%20%24600%20For%20Sex%20Services%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHan%20Lee%20charged%20sex%20buyers%20%24350%20to%20%24600%20per%20hour%20depending%20on%20the%20services%20and%20only%20took%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20allegedly%20advertised%20their%20prostitution%20network%20and%20offered%20appointments%20with%20women%20via%20two%20websites.%20Both%20websites%20purported%20to%20advertise%20nude%20models%20for%20professional%20photography%20at%20upscale%20studios%20as%20a%20front%20for%20prostitution%20offered%20through%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20further%20alleged%20that%20Han%20Lee%20maintained%20local%20brothel%20phone%20numbers%20which%20they%20used%20to%20communicate%20with%20verified%20customers%20and%20schedule%20appointments%20via%20text%20messages%3B%20send%20customers%20a%20%26quot%3Bmenu%26quot%3B%20of%20available%20options%20at%20the%20brothel%2C%20including%20the%20women%20and%20sexual%20services%20available%20and%20the%20hourly%20rate%3B%20and%20to%20text%20customers%20directions%20to%20the%20brothel's%20location%20where%20they%20engaged%20in%20commercial%20sex%20with%20the%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20conceal%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20prostitution%20network%2C%20Han%20Lee%20deposited%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20of%20cash%20proceeds%20into%20personal%20and%20third-party%20bank%20accounts%20and%20peer-to-peer%20transfers%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20alleged%20that%20they%20regularly%20used%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20of%20the%20cash%20proceeds%20from%20the%20prostitution%20business%20to%20purchase%20money%20orders%20(in%20values%20under%20an%20amount%20that%20would%20trigger%20reporting%20and%20identification%20requirements)%20to%20conceal%20the%20source%20of%20the%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20money%20orders%20were%20then%20used%20to%20pay%20for%20rent%20and%20utilities%20at%20brothel%20locations%20in%20Massachusetts%20and%20Virginia%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20clients%20have%20so%20far%20not%20been%20identified%20but%20authorities%20have%20estimated%20the%20network's%20customer%20base%20was%20in%20the%20hundreds%20and%20included%20elected%20officials%2C%20pharmaceutical%20and%20technology%20executives%2C%20doctors%2C%20military%20officers%2C%20professors%2C%20lawyers%2C%20business%20executives%2C%20scientists%20and%20accountants.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727594880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgnp7hqdo_sex-racket_625x300_29_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhan-lee-how-us-woman-ran-a-sex-racket-for-politicians-military-officers-lawyers-6674897%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Han%20Lee%2C%2042%2C%20has%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20running%20a%20high-end%20sex%20racket%20in%20the%20greater%20Boston%20area%20and%20the%20suburbs%20of%20Washington.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhan-lee-how-us-woman-ran-a-sex-racket-for-politicians-military-officers-lawyers-6674897%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Smashed%20you%20enough...'%3A%20When%20Virat%20silenced%20Faulkner%20with%20a%20savage%20reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727594415000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113782288%2Cimgsize-42202.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Five-smashed-you-enough-in-my-life-when-virat-kohli-silenced-james-faulkner-with-a-savage-reply%2Farticleshow%2F11378