%20campground%20in%20Rogers%2C%20where%20Darien%20Urban%2C%2021%2C%20and%20Shalene%20Ehlers%2C%20and%20their%20baby%20have%20been%20living%20for%20approximately%20three%20months.%20Rogers%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20Ozarks%20near%20the%20borders%20of%20Oklahoma%20and%20Missouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20condition%20of%20the%20baby%20was%20not%20immediately%20known%20as%20of%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20affidavit%20obtained%20by%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Fnation%2F2024%2F09%2F26%2Farkansas-couple-sell-baby-for-money-beer-allegations%2F75393884007%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20USA%20TODAY%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20deputies%20were%20called%20to%20Beaver%20Lake%20Hide%20Away%20Campground%20on%20September%2021%20after%20a%20report%20from%20someone%20in%20the%20manager's%20office%20claimed%20the%20couple%20was%20attempting%20to%20give%20their%20baby%20away%20in%20exchange%20for%20money%20and%20beer.%20The%20caller%20also%20informed%20authorities%20that%20the%20baby%20required%20medical%20attention%20due%20to%20observed%20rashes%20and%20blisters%20around%20the%20child's%20buttocks%20and%20genitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20deputies%20arrived%2C%20a%20detective%20noted%20in%20the%20affidavit%20that%20the%20couple%20was%20not%20present%2C%20and%20the%20baby%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20children's%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20states%20that%20one%20witness%20approached%20the%20couple's%20camper%2C%20asked%20to%20take%20the%20baby%20overnight%2C%20and%20provided%20the%20couple%20with%20beers.%20The%20man%20told%20deputies%20that%20the%20couple%20agreed%2C%20so%20he%20took%20the%20baby%20out%20of%20concern%20for%20his%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20witness%2C%20a%20woman%20at%20the%20campground%2C%20also%20took%20the%20baby%2C%20changed%20his%20diaper%2C%20and%20bathed%20him.%20She%20captured%20photos%20of%20the%20blisters%20and%20rash%20to%20present%20to%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn-site%2C%20deputies%20found%20a%20letter%20allegedly%20signed%20by%20the%20couple%2C%20agreeing%20to%20accept%20a%20cashier's%20check%20for%20%241%2C000%20on%20Monday%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20child.%20The%20letter%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BI%2C%20Darien%20Urban%20and%20Shalene%20Ehlers%20are%20signing%20our%20rights%20over%20to%20Cody%20Nathaniel%20Martin%20of%20our%20baby%20boy%20%5Bredacted%5D%20for%20%241%2C000%20on%2009%2F21%2F2024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20reads.%20%26quot%3BDisclaimer%3A%20After%20signing%20this%20there%20will%20be%20no%20changing%20yall%20two's%20minds%20and%20to%20never%20contact%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetectives%20also%20obtained%20cellphone%20video%20of%20both%20parents%20signing%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20interview%20with%20detectives%2C%20the%20couple%20claimed%20their%20baby%20%26quot%3Bwas%20undergoing%20an%20adoption%26quot%3B%20and%20stated%20they%20recorded%20the%20video%20because%20they%20planned%20to%20finalize%20the%20adoption%20on%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputies%20arrested%20the%20couple%20and%20booked%20them%20into%20local%20jail%20on%20charges%20of%20felony%20endangering%20the%20welfare%20of%20a%20child%20and%20attempted%20relinquishment%20of%20a%20minor%20for%20adoption.%20A%20judge%20set%20their%20bond%20at%20%2450%2C000%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20and%20jail%20records%20indicated%20that%20both%20defendants%20were%20released%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20are%20scheduled%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20on%20October%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727587380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fc5tk702o_darien-urban-and-shalene-ehlers_625x300_29_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-couple-accused-of-trying-to-sell-their-baby-for-1-000-and-beer-6675022%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20a