bi-annual%20shift%20of%20government%20offices%2C%20including%20the%20secretariat%2C%20between%20Jammu%20and%20Srinagar%20in%20view%20of%20the%20harsh%20winter%20in%20J-K.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20protect%20your%20rights%2C%20your%20rights%20to%20your%20land%20and%20your%20employment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Gandhi%20while%20speaking%20in%20support%20of%20the%20party%20candidate%20in%20Bishnah%2C%20Neeraj%20Kundan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20Amit%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20the%20statehood%20issue%2C%20she%20said%20%26quot%3BI%20found%20it%20amusing%20when%20the%20home%20minister%20said%20in%20his%20speech%20that%20if%20you%20want%20statehood%20back%2C%20you%20must%20vote%20for%20us.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%2C%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20took%20it%20away.%20It%20is%20like%20a%20thief%20who%20steals%20your%20TV%20and%20then%20says%2C%20'If%20you%20want%20it%20back%2C%20ask%20me.'%20%26quot%3BThey%20claim%20only%20they%20can%20return%20it.%20If%20our%20government%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20we%20will%20immediately%20restore%20your%20statehood%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20government%20for%20%26quot%3Bdowngrading%26quot%3B%20J-K%20into%20a%20Union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20country.%20Nature%20has%20given%20you%20everything-these%20resources%2C%20this%20beauty.%20From%20here%20came%20the%20great%20sages%20who%20spread%20faith%2C%20culture%20and%20teachings%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20in%20other%20countries%20too.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20BJP%20has%20snatched%20everything%20you%20have%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20her%20grandmother%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20bond%26quot%3B%20with%20Kashmir%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFour%20or%20five%20days%20before%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination%2C%20she%20told%20us%20she%20wanted%20to%20visit%20Kashmir%20and%20see%20the%20autumn%20leaves.%20She%20brought%20us%20to%20the%20Kheer%20Bhawani%20temple%2C%20and%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20returning%20to%20Delhi%2C%20she%20was%20assassinated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20call%20from%20her%20land%20and%20Mata%20that%20took%20her%20to%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20reminisced%2C%20emphasising%20her%20family's%20longstanding%20relationship%20with%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20also%20attacked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20her%20speech%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20not%20serious%20about%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%20of%20J-K.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20have%20turned%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20a%20pawn%20in%20their%20political%20chess%20game%20as%20policies%20are%20not%20being%20made%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20region%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20created%20to%20stir%20emotions%20across%20the%20country%20using%20you%20and%20serve%20political%20purposes%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20in%20Modi%20Ji's%20speech%2C%20there%20was%20no%20seriousness%20about%20the%20genuine%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Fixing%20railway%20stations%20is%20not%20an%20achievement%20to%20boast%20about%20when%20the%20bigger%20issues%20of%20your%20rights%2C%20land%2C%20and%20employment%20are%20being%20ignored%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20really%20matters%20are%20the%20genuine%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%20of%20J-K.%20Why%20aren't%20those%20being%20addressed%3F%20Why%20aren't%20they%20focusing%20on%20the%20truth%3F%20When%20did%20the%20prime%20minister%20take%20away%20your%20state's%20status%3F%20The%20Congress%20leader%20also%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20in%20her%20speech%2C%20claiming%20that%20half%20of%20the%20contracts%20meant%20for%20J-K%20had%20been%20awarded%20to%20outsiders.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20been%20deprived%20of%20your%20voting%20rights%2C%20and%20small%20businesses%20are%20being%20crushed%20by%20large%20corporations.%20Why%20is%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20lagging%20behind%20in%20employment%3F%20Why%20is%20there%20so%20much%20unemployment%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20BJP%20government%2C%20she%20said%2C%20has%20established%20a%20%26quot%3Bsystem%20of%20loot%2C%20with%20a%20puppet%20government%20running%20things%20by%20remote%20control%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLand%20banks%20are%20being%20created%2C%20and%20your%20lands%20are%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20big%20industrialists%2C%20the%20same%20ones%20whom%20Modi%20Ji%20has%20favoured%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20same%20is%20happening%20here%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20government%20on%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20introduced%20Agniveer%2C%20a%20scheme%20that%20gives%20nothing%20to%20those%20who%20risk%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20borders%20and%20become%20martyrs.%20This%20is%20why%20all%20opposition%20parties%20are%20fighting%20and%20raising%20this%20issue%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20government%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20are%20so%20arrogant%20that%20even%20though%20they%20know%20the%20scheme%20is%20wrong%20and%20not%20beneficial%20for%20the%20youth%2C%20they%20refuse%20to%20back%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20touched%20on%20the%20drug%20addiction%20problem%20plaguing%20the%20region%2C%20saying%20that%20no%20BJP%20leader%20talks%20about%20it%20because%20they%20know%20the%20root%20cause%20is%20unemployment.%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20joblessness%2C%20people%20are%20falling%20prey%20to%20the%20drug%20mafia%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20called%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20vote%20wisely%2C%20underlining%20that%20the%20Congress's%20vision%20includes%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%2C%20protection%20of%20land%20rights%20of%20locals%2C%20and%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727584200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fk6b04ljo_indira-gandhi-priyanka-gandhi_625x300_29_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-elections-2024-priyanka-recalls-kashmir-trip-with-indira-gandhi-days-before-her-assassination-6671289%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20will%20restore%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20statehood%2C%20party%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%20on%20Saturday%20while%20she%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20for%20using%20the%20Union%20territory%20as%20a%20pawn%20to%20%26quot%3Bstir%20emotions%26quot%3B%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-elections-2024-priyanka-recalls-kashmir-trip-with-indira-gandhi-days-before-her-assassination-6671289%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BCCI's%20Blow%20To%20Overseas%20Stars%2C%20Starc%20Rs%2024.75%20Crore%20Salary%20No%20More%20Possible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20has%20introduced%20significant%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20auctions%20are%20conducted%2C%20especially%20with%20regards%20to%20overseas%20players.%20In%20the%20IPL%202024%20auction%2C%20Starc%20shattered%20all%20records%2C%20becoming%20the%20most%20expensive%20player%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20T20%20league%2C%20after%20being%20roped%20in%20for%20INR%2024.75%20crore%20by%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%20However%2C%20such%20a%20situation%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20possible%2C%20at%20least%20from%20the%20player's%20point%20of%20view.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%202025%20auction%2C%20BCCI%20proposed%20a%20new%20regulation%20that%20would%20make%20overseas%20players%20ineligible%20to%20earn%20more%20money%20than%20those%20sold%20or%20retained%20in%20the%20mega%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarc%20marked%20his%20IPL%20return%20in%20the%202024%20season%2C%20making%20him%20available%20for%20the%20mini-auction%2C%20where%20he%20fetched%20a%20record-breaking%20price%20from%20the%20Knight%20Riders.%20However%2C%20his%20return%20to%20the%20T20%20league%20was%20also%20met%20with%20criticism%2C%20with%20critics%20suggesting%20that%20certain%20overseas%20players%20only%20make%20themselves%20available%20for%20mini-auction%2C%20with%20the%20attempt%20being%20to%20cash-in%20on%20the%20skewed%20demand-supply%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20IPL%202025%20season%20onwards%2C%20however%2C%20that%20wouldn't%20be%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F131787%2Fipl-auction-explainer-rtm-with-a-twist-retention-slabs-and-cap-on-foreign-player-fees%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20overseas%20player%20will%20have%20to%20register%20himself%20for%20the%20mega%20auction%20(2025)%2C%20if%20he%20is%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20IPL%202026%20and%20IPL%202027%20seasons.%20Space%20for%20a%20few%20exceptions%20have%20also%20been%20made%2C%20for%20cases%20where%20the%20player%20is%20either%20injured%20or%20has%20a%20medical%20condition.%20But%20such%20a%20scenario%20would%20need%20to%20be%20confirmed%20by%20the%20home%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overseas%20players%20will%20also%20have%20a%20salary%20cap%20in%20the%20IPL%202026%20auction.%20The%20maximum%20fee%20an%20overseas%20player%20can%20earn%20in%20the%20mini-auction%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20highest%20retention%20fee%20of%20a%20player%20or%20the%20price%20another%20player%20manages%20to%20fetch%20in%20the%20mega-auction.%20The%20amount%20lower%20between%20the%20two%20will%20be%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExample%3A%20If%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20retained%20by%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20for%20a%20fee%20of%20INR%2018%20crores%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Deepak%20Chahar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F60022-deepak-lokandersingh-chahar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDeepak%20Chahar%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20bought%20for%20a%20fee%20of%20INR%2015%20crore%20during%20the%202025%20mega%20auction%2C%20then%20no%20overseas%20player%20would%20be%20eligible%20to%20earn%20more%20than%20INR%2015%20crore%20in%20the%20subsequent%20mini-auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20case%20where%20Deepak%20Chahar%20is%20signed%20in%20the%20mega%20auction%20for%20INR%2020%20crores%2C%20then%20the%20maximum%20amount%20an%20overseas%20player%20can%20stand%20to%20earn%20would%20be%20INR%2018%20crore%20(Virat%20Kohli's%20retention%20fee).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20franchises%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20bid%20for%20as%20long%20as%20they%20like%2C%20the%20additional%20amount%20(over%20and%20above%2018%20crore%20or%2015%20crore%2C%20as%20explained%20above)%2C%20would%20go%20to%20BCCI's%20bank%20account%20and%20not%20the%20player's.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727583660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fnj4c41qo_mitchell-starc-bcci_625x300_29_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fipl-2025-auction-bccis-blow-to-overseas-stars-mitchell-starc-rs-24-75-crore-situation-no-more-possible-6674720%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20bought%20Mitchell%20Starc%20for%20INR%2024.75%20crore%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20mini-auction.%20However%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20possible%20for%20Starc%20to%20earn%20such%20an%20amount%20in%20the%20same%20situation%20anymore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fipl-2025-auction-bccis-blow-to-overseas-stars-mitchell-starc-rs-24-75-crore-situation-no-more-possible-6674720%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gurugram%20Cops%20File%20Case%20Against%20WhatsApp%20Directors%20For%20Not%20Providing%20Info%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGurugram%20police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20WhatsApp's%20directors%20and%20nodal%20officers%20after%20the%20messaging%20app%20refused%20to%20provide%20information%20about%20three%20accounts%20linked%20to%20an%20investigation.%20The%20case%20invokes%20sections%20relating%20to%20disobeying%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20a%20public%20servant%2C%20concealing%20an%20offender%20to%20screen%20him%20from%20legal%20punishment%20and%20destruction%20of%20any%20document%20or%20electronic%20record%20that%20may%20have%20to%20be%20produced%20as%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20an%20Inspector%20in%20the%20cyber%20police%20station.%20The%20complaint%20cited%20a%20May%2027%20FIR%20under%20cheating%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%20charges.%20As%20part%20of%20its%20investigation%2C%20Gurugram%20police%20asked%20WhatsApp%20for%20information%20on%20four%20numbers%20used%20by%20the%20accused.%20A%20notice%20was%20sent%20to%20WhatsApp%20on%20July%2017%20via%20email.%20%26quot%3BOn%2019.07.2024%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20in%20a%20deliberate%20act%20of%20non-compliance%2C%20raised%20objections%2C%20seeking%20clarification%20regarding%20the%20specific%20nature%C2%A0of%20the%20criminal%20activities%20allegedly%20perpetrated%20using%20these%20identified%20numbers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2025%2C%20the%20police%20sent%20a%20detailed%20response%2C%20reiterating%20the%20demand%20for%20disclosure%20of%20the%20requisite%20information%20for%20the%20specified%20mobile%20numbers%2C%20%26quot%3Bthus%20underscoring%20the%20necessity%20for%20the%20cooperation%20of%20WhatsApp%20in%20this%20investigation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatsApp%20presented%20further%20objections.%20A%20comprehensive%20response%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20exigency%20implicated%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20was%20furnished%20on%2023.08.2024.%20It%20was%20explicitly%20stated%20that%20the%20matter%20warranted%20immediate%20action%20due%20to%20the%20grave%20concerns%20surrounding%20investigation.%20However%2C%20despite%20due%20diligence%20and%20lawful%20requests%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20on%2028.08.2024%2C%20rejected%20the%20legitimate%20requisition.%20This%20refusal%20constitutes%20an%20overt%20act%20of%20disregard%20for%20statutory%20obligations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20refusal%20of%20WhatsApp%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20lawfully%20promulgated%20orders%20by%20public%20authorities%20and%20their%20denial%20in%20furnishing%20the%20requested%20information%2C%20despite%20being%20legally%20mandated%20to%20do%20so%20under%20the%20prevailing%20laws%20of%20the%20land%2C%20constitutes%20a%20willful%20and%20contumacious%20disobedience%20of%20legal%20directives%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%C2%A0%26quot%3BBy%20not%20rendering%20the%20information%20as%20solicited%2C%20WhatsApp%20appears%20to%20have%20knowingly%20abetted%20the%20accused%20individuals%2C%20thereby%20engaging%20in%20deliberate%20suppression%20and%20obstruction%20of%20critical%20electronic%20evidence.%20This%20conduct%20amounts%20to%20a%20violation%20of%20statutory%20provisions%20designed%20to%20preserve%20and%20facilitate%20the%20administration%20of%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20police%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20under%20Bharatiya%20Nyah%20Sanhita%20and%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%20The%20FIR%20names%20one%20Krishna%20Choudhary%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20messaging%20app%2C%20which%20has%20nearly%203%20billion%20unique%20users%20globally%2C%20it%20discloses%20account%20records%20solely%20in%20accordance%20with%20our%20terms%20of%20service%20and%20applicable%20law.%20%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20we%20will%20assess%20whether%20requests%20are%20consistent%20with%20internationally%20recognized%20standards.%20These%20include%20human%20rights%2C%20due%20process%2C%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says%20in%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727583120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fcjrkqk7g_whatsapp_625x300_18_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurugram-cops-file-case-against-whatsapp-directors-for-not-providing-info-6674661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gurugram%20police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20WhatsApp's%20directors%20and%20nodal%20officers%20after%20the%20messaging%20app%20refused%20to%20provide%20information%20about%20three%20accounts%20linked%20to%20an%20investigation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurugram-cops-file-case-against-whatsapp-directors-for-not-providing-info-6674661%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jean%20Smart%20Sings%2C%20Jokes%20About%20Eric%20Adams%20and%20Declares%20%E2%80%98Lesbians%20Are%20Obsessed%20With%20Me%E2%80%99%20in%20%E2%80%98SNL%E2%80%99%20Monologue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727582827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fdownload-10-e1727582534174.jpeg%3Fcrop%3D0px%252C19px%252C923px%252C519px%26resize%3D1000%252C563%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236159172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CSaturday%20Night%20Live%E2%80%9D%20host%20Jean%20Smart%20kicked%