20Right-To-Match%20cards.%20But%2C%20the%20board%20also%20made%20it%20mandatory%20for%20the%20franchises%20to%20retain%20at%20least%20one%20uncapped%20player%2C%20if%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20exhaust%20all%206%20retention%20options.%20However%2C%20the%20RTM%20option%20this%20auction%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20ones%2C%20is%20quite%20tricky%20in%20its%20implementation.%20There%20were%20some%20who%20had%20expressed%20disappointment%20at%20RTM's%20potential%20return%20in%20IPL%202025%20auction.%20Hence%2C%20the%20BCCI%20has%20made%20its%20implementation%20less%20rewarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20franchise%20that%20released%20a%20certain%20player%20could%20use%20the%20RTM%20card%20to%20buy%20back%20a%20player%20who%20was%20won%20by%20another%20franchise%20during%20the%20bidding%20war%20at%20the%20IPL%20auction.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20upcoming%20mega%20auction%2C%20just%20showing%20an%20RTM%20card%20won't%20be%20enough%20for%20a%20franchise%20to%20buy%20the%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20franchise%20shows%20the%20RTM%20card%2C%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20a%20bidding%20war%20between%20two%20different%20franchises%2C%20the%20team%20which%20had%20won%20the%20said%20bidding%20would%20be%20given%20another%20opportunity%20to%20increase%20the%20bid%20for%20a%20said%20player.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20the%20team%20holding%20the%20RTM%20card%20would%20have%20the%20option%20to%20withdraw%20or%20match%20the%20improved%20bid%20for%20the%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20highest%20bidder%20will%20be%20given%20one%20final%20opportunity%20to%20raise%20their%20bid%20for%20a%20player%20before%20the%20team%20holding%20the%20RTM%20card%20can%20exercise%20their%20right.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20Team%201%20holds%20the%20RTM%20for%20Player%20X%20and%20Team%202%20has%20placed%20the%20highest%20bid%20of%20Rs.%206%20Cr%2C%20then%20Team%201%20will%20be%20first%20asked%20if%20they%20will%20exercise%20RTM%20if%20Team%201%20agrees%2C%20then%20Team%202%20will%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20increase%20their%20bid.%20If%20Team%202%20raises%20their%20bid%20to%20Rs.%209%20Cr%2C%20then%20Team%201%20can%20use%20the%20RTM%20and%20acquire%20Player%20X%20for%20Rs.%209%20Cr.%20If%20Team%202%20chooses%20not%20to%20raise%20the%20bid%20and%20keeps%20it%20at%20Rs.%206%20Cr%2C%20Team%201%20can%20use%20the%20RTM%20and%20get%20Player%20X%20for%20Rs.%206%20Cr%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rule%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExample%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0If%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Faf%20du%20Plessis%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1579-faf-du-plessis-playerprofile%5C%22%3EFaf%20du%20Plessis%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20being%20auctioned%2C%20CSK%20places%20the%20highest%20bid%2C%20then%20his%20current%20franchise%20(RCB)%20will%20be%20asked%20if%20they%20wish%20to%20use%20RTM.%20If%20RCB%20agrees%2C%20then%20CSK%20will%20be%20given%20one%20more%20chance%20to%20increase%20the%20final%20bid.%20Then%2C%20RCB%20can%20use%20their%20RTM%20and%20re-sign%20Du%20Plessis%20or%20choose%20to%20withdraw.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727581200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fqphokji_dc-ipl-auction-bcci_625x300_29_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fexplained-how-revamped-rtm-rule-will-be-implemented-in-ipl-2025-auction-6674553%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BCCI%20introduced%20a%20revamped%20RTM%20rule%20which%20franchises%20can%20use%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20mega%20auction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fexplained-how-revamped-rtm-rule-will-be-implemented-in-ipl-2025-auction-6674553%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98SNL%E2%80%99%20Reveals%20Jim%20Gaffigan%20as%20Tim%20Walz%2C%20Andy%20Samberg%20as%20Doug%20Emhoff%20in%20Cold%20Open%20With%20Maya%20Rudolph%E2%80%99s%20Ka