stry%2C%20which%20people%20are%20gradually%20forgetting.%20Bamboo%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20buildings%20constructed%20within%20Tieedi%20as%20well.%20As%20I%20prepare%20to%20leave%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20greeted%20by%20Riwash%2C%20whose%20words%20I%20will%20carry%20home%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNature%20is%20important%3B%20it%20is%20absolute.%20We%20must%20learn%20to%20live%20in%20harmony%20with%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727450449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8112_11zon-1727442672.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Utsow%20Pradhan%2C%20founder%20of%20Tieedi%2C%20left%20his%20corporate%20job%20to%20restore%20his%20ancestral%20land%20in%20Darjeeling%2C%20which%20had%20turned%20into%20a%20dumping%20ground.%20Through%20zero-waste%20initiatives%2C%20eco-trails%2C%20and%20community%20involvement%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20creating%20sustainable%20villages%2C%20reviving%20local%20traditions%2C%20and%20helping%20restore%20the%20fragile%20Himalayan%20ecosystem.%20%E2%80%98Tieedi%2C%E2%80%99%20an%20acronym%20for%20%E2%80%9CTake%20It%20Easy%2C%20Easy%20Does%20It.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arunava%20Banerjee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367839%2Fdarjeeling-man-creating-zero-waste-villages-through-permaculture-and-waste-management%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20This%20Domestic%20Help%E2%80%99s%20Love%20for%20Dance%20Led%20to%205.8M%20Insta%20Followers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20her%20early%20life%2C%20Varsha%20Solanki%E2%80%99s%20world%20revolved%20around%20the%20harsh%20realities%20of%20poverty.%20On%20an%20ordinary%20day%2C%20she%20would%20accompany%20her%20mother%2C%20a%20domestic%20help%2C%20to%20clean%