20his%20focus%20on%20village%20development%20to%20female%20foeticide.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20imagined%20this%20path%20for%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reminisces%2C%20thinking%20back%20to%20his%20days%20as%20a%20mathematics%20coach%20in%20his%20early%2020s%20when%20working%20Sundays%20and%20the%20extra%20money%20was%20all%20he%20looked%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20youth%20with%20simple%20dreams%2C%20Jaglan%20has%20grown%20into%20the%20proud%20father%20of%20two%20daughters%3B%20teaching%20India%E2%80%99s%20generation%20of%20men%20to%20be%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20baby%20girl%20melts%20a%20patriarch%E2%80%99s%20heart%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20every%20question%20I%20pose%20to%20Jaglan%2C%20I%20can%20hear%20two%20background%20voices%20nudging%20him%20when%20he%20muddles%20the%20details.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20school%20holiday%20for%20Nandini%20(12)%20and%20Yachika%20(10).%20Naturally%2C%20they%20have%20picked%20a%20spot%20beside%20their%20father%20for%20the%20interview.%20Having%20had%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335631%2Fassam-jorhat-transwoman-opens-free-libraries-for-queer-positivity-lgbt-empowerment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactivism%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20duo%20are%20well-versed%20in%20the%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COften%2C%20they%20have%20also%20joined%20me%20in%20their%20own%20scope%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaglan%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20anecdotes%20of%20how%20Nandini%20would%20urge%20her%20school%20friends%20to%20avoid%20using%20%3Cem%3Egaalis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Hindi%20swear%20words)%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20those%20that%20referenced%20women%20%E2%80%94%20in%20tandem%20with%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20launch%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Gaali%20Bandh%20Ghar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20campaign%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-imag