irl-child-female-foeticide-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eawareness%20about%20girl%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20inequalities%20they%20have%20to%20endure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaglan%20recalls%20the%20day%20as%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20of%20his%20life.%20But%20the%20nurse%20and%20doctor%20at%20the%20hospital%20begged%20to%20differ.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20nurse%20delivered%20the%20news%20to%20me%20that%20I%20had%20become%20a%20father%2C%20I%20gave%20her%20a%20token%20as%20a%20thank-you%20gesture.%20She%20declined.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20doctor%20will%20get%20angry.%20If%20you%20had%20a%20boy%2C%20we%20would%20accept%20it%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dismissed%20this%20as%20a%20one-off%20incident%2C%20refusing%20to%20let%20it%20spoil%20his%20celebratory%20mood.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20I%20started%20distributing%20sweets%20in%20the%20village%2C%20I%20realised%20there%20was%20a%20serious%20problem.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20people%20would%20assume%20that%20my%20distributing%20sweets%20meant%20I%20had%20a%20baby%20boy.%20So%20they%20would%20congratulate%20me%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%20When%20Jaglan%20told%20them%20he%20had%20become%20a%20father%20to%20a%20baby%20girl%2C%20their%20responses%20were%20usually%20consolatory.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKoi%20baat%20nahi%2C%20agli%20baar%20ladka%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Don%E2%80%99t%20worry.%20Next%20time%20you%20will%20get%20a%20son).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FrA-F2BWnHmk%3Fsi%3DN_7a_Xus1lNQBnDd%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20how%20would%20Jaglan%20respond%20to%20these%20unwarranted%20sympathies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20and%20bought%20more%20%3Cem%3Emithai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20celebrated%20for%20a%20